1
00:01:43,312 --> 00:01:44,646
少爷！准备好了
Young master, we are ready

2
00:02:26,021 --> 00:02:26,647
辛苦了！少爷
What's a hard job for you, young master

3
00:02:26,647 --> 00:02:28,190
少爷！擦个汗吧
The towel, young master

4
00:02:37,074 --> 00:02:38,367
师爷，少爷写的是甚么？
What did he write?

5
00:02:38,617 --> 00:02:39,493
名字
His name!

6
00:02:39,951 --> 00:02:44,039
好棒！原来少爷会写自己的名字
Great! Young master knows how to write his name!

7
00:02:44,331 --> 00:02:45,749
对呀
Yes!

8
00:02:51,296 --> 00:02:52,172
好字
Nice calligraphy

9
00:02:53,340 --> 00:02:54,466
走开
Get lost

10
00:02:56,635 --> 00:03:01,765
好字！龙飞凤舞，苏察哈尔灿
Nice calligraphy! So Cha Ha Yee Chan!

11
00:03:01,932 --> 00:03:02,766
你念反了，老爷
It's reversed, Master

12
00:03:03,392 --> 00:03:05,060
灿尔哈察苏
Chan Yee Ha Cha So

13
00:03:05,227 --> 00:03:09,022
好小子，但是别骄傲，知道吗？
Good boy, but, don't be proud! Got me?

14
00:03:11,024 --> 00:03:13,860
爹，我们苏察哈尔家
Dad, since the first emperor of the Ching Dynasty,

15
00:03:14,194 --> 00:03:15,654
自太祖皇帝到现在
our family

16
00:03:15,654 --> 00:03:17,447
都没有几个会写字的
has been illiterate

17
00:03:17,614 --> 00:03:20,742
现在可不同，我的儿子你的孙儿阿灿
But not, my son, that's your grandson,

18
00:03:20,867 --> 00:03:22,536
他会写自己的名字
he knows how to write his name!

19
00:03:22,744 --> 00:03:25,872
爹，这可是非同少可
Dad, it's very great!

20
00:03:26,623 --> 00:03:27,916
今天会写字
He knows writing now,

21
00:03:27,916 --> 00:03:29,710
他朝必成大学士
he will be scholar one day

22
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:31,336
今天会写名
Now, he knows how to write his name,

23
00:03:31,378 --> 00:03:33,088
他日一定会生子
he will have a son later

24
00:03:33,171 --> 00:03:35,799
少爷，你真是要好好地学习写字
Young master, you should try hard to learn

25
00:03:35,882 --> 00:03:38,051
阿灿，先把它裱起来
Chan, I think, we should mount it

26
00:03:38,093 --> 00:03:38,719
裱起它
OK

27
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:40,971
师爷，把它挂在最当眼的地方
Professor, show it in some obvious places

28
00:03:41,012 --> 00:03:42,222
这样吧，师爷
By the way, one minute,

29
00:03:42,264 --> 00:03:45,100
你先揹著它簪花挂红，游行威风一下
why don't you carry it with traditional decoration in the street?

30
00:03:45,350 --> 00:03:46,393
走吧
Let's go!

31
00:03:46,435 --> 00:03:48,812
阿灿，来⋯坐⋯
Chan, come and sit…

32
00:03:49,479 --> 00:03:52,232
你这么争气，我也很安慰
I am so pleased that you are that hard working and filial

33
00:03:52,482 --> 00:03:56,069
你听我说，爹是有名的败家儿
Listen to me, I am notorious of being a spendthrift

34
00:03:56,319 --> 00:03:58,697
家里的财产也败得差不多
My fortune is almost used up

35
00:03:58,947 --> 00:04:01,783
说难听一点，日后我两脚一伸
If I die one day,

36
00:04:01,867 --> 00:04:03,160
你个王八蛋，怎么到这里来讨饭？
you should depend on yourself

37
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:04,536
向来我都是靠自己
I used to depend on myself

38
00:04:05,996 --> 00:04:07,998
十万两一张，省一点花啊
The cheques worth 100,000 taels! Don't be an extravagant spender

39
00:04:08,540 --> 00:04:10,375
茂利，把我的西洋帽拿来
Give me the imported hat

40
00:04:10,542 --> 00:04:11,293
你去哪，阿灿？
Where are you going? Chan!

41
00:04:12,461 --> 00:04:13,712
今晚我做大寿
I am having a grand birthday party tonight

42
00:04:14,546 --> 00:04:15,172
你贵庚？
How old are you?

43
00:04:15,464 --> 00:04:17,632
廿五岁大寿，早点到
25 years old. Come earlier

44
00:04:18,717 --> 00:04:20,927
做大寿你也得先把头发梳整齐
But you should dress up first

45
00:04:20,927 --> 00:04:22,596
老是一个乞丐的模样
You are like beggar!

46
00:04:23,013 --> 00:04:25,182
乞丐会那么有钱？我也想当
How can a beggar be that rich?! I do want to be a rich beggar!

47
00:04:27,809 --> 00:04:29,728
那寿头真是⋯
That fat-headed…

48
00:04:29,728 --> 00:04:30,771
过来，过来
Come over here

49
00:04:30,854 --> 00:04:32,022
老爷，甚么事？
What's the matter?

50
00:04:32,439 --> 00:04:35,317
那臭小子的寿帖真威风
The invitation card of my son is great!

51
00:04:35,734 --> 00:04:38,361
他日老爷做大寿，要比他威风
If I hold a birthday party in future, I want a better invitation card!

52
00:04:57,714 --> 00:05:00,967
皇爷，你觉得广东大戏怎样？
Your Majesty, how do you think about the Cantonese Opera?

53
00:05:02,052 --> 00:05:05,013
地方戏曲，当然不及京戏
For sure, it can't compete with Peking Opera!

54
00:05:05,472 --> 00:05:07,849
但也算是一种见识
But, I appreciate viewing this

55
00:05:11,978 --> 00:05:16,233
打赏⋯打赏
Money…

56
00:05:16,274 --> 00:05:17,776
恭喜苏翁生辰快乐
Happy birthday to you, Mr So

57
00:05:17,818 --> 00:05:20,153
我家破人亡、贫病老弱
I am homeless and sick…

58
00:05:20,195 --> 00:05:23,907
无亲无故、妻离子散
I am poor, I am damn poor!

59
00:05:23,949 --> 00:05:25,575
打赏个救命钱　　怎么搅的，死乞丐！
- Please give me some money    - Kidding? Damn you beggar!

60
00:05:25,992 --> 00:05:28,662
你个王八蛋，怎么到这裏来讨饭？
How can you beg here?

61
00:05:28,745 --> 00:05:29,913
我打⋯
Go to hell!

62
00:05:29,913 --> 00:05:31,706
打赏　　是，少爷
- Give him tips    - Yes, young master

63
00:05:32,499 --> 00:05:34,417
这样也有打赏？
Are you kidding? How can you give him tips?

64
00:05:35,752 --> 00:05:36,545
乞丐也是人
A beggar is a man too

65
00:05:36,837 --> 00:05:38,213
只要有钱的都可以来
Everyone can come here if he has money

66
00:05:38,505 --> 00:05:39,297
你这个月来这里
Your living,

67
00:05:39,297 --> 00:05:41,550
吃饭看戏宵夜嫖妓，我包
including the expenditure for hooking, I will pay for you!

68
00:05:41,716 --> 00:05:42,509
你包？
You pay it?

69
00:05:42,551 --> 00:05:43,343
不可以吗？
So what?

70
00:05:44,761 --> 00:05:46,596
可以，可以
Nothing!

71
00:05:46,596 --> 00:05:49,224
大爷进我间房吧⋯　　请你跟我来
- Come into my room…    - Please follow me.

72
00:05:51,184 --> 00:05:53,228
苏⋯翁
Mr So!

73
00:05:53,311 --> 00:05:54,396
是⋯
Hello…

74
00:05:54,604 --> 00:05:55,522
你好吗，鸨母？
How are you, Madam Pimp?

75
00:05:55,939 --> 00:05:58,149
你真坏，有名字你不叫，叫我鸨母
It's very bad of you to call me that!

76
00:05:58,400 --> 00:05:59,651
大家坦白一点不好吗？
Just be frank, why not?

77
00:05:59,901 --> 00:06:00,819
要坦白吗
You should be frank!

78
00:06:01,194 --> 00:06:03,780
你的帽子像披麻带孝似的
Your hat, is like the mourning uniform!

79
00:06:03,780 --> 00:06:04,906
你老爸死了吗？
Has your dad passed away?

80
00:06:06,324 --> 00:06:09,119
这样说大家才开心嘛
I feel happy to talk in this way

81
00:06:09,786 --> 00:06:12,914
赵先生这趟帮本官扫平长毛贼
Mr Chiu, you helped me to terminate the Hairy Gang,

82
00:06:13,164 --> 00:06:15,417
皇上一定重重有赏
the emperor will give you award for this

83
00:06:15,959 --> 00:06:17,878
那就有劳皇爷在皇上面前
I'll appreciate it if you

84
00:06:17,878 --> 00:06:19,212
多说几句好说话
speak something nice in front of the emperor

85
00:06:20,463 --> 00:06:22,465
大戏做完了，请用毛巾
Please have the towel

86
00:06:25,844 --> 00:06:28,013
苏翁来了⋯
Mr So has come

87
00:06:28,847 --> 00:06:30,849
苏翁，恭喜发财
Congratulations!

88
00:06:30,891 --> 00:06:31,850
这边⋯这边
This way…

89
00:06:31,850 --> 00:06:34,269
苏翁，今天是你的好日子，很高兴吧
Mr So, today is your big day, you must be very happy!

90
00:06:34,519 --> 00:06:36,646
我们有几位新来的姑娘，保证你满意
We have some new girls, you must be satisfied with them

91
00:06:36,688 --> 00:06:37,772
金鱼还是木鱼？
What are they? Gold fish, or cooked fish?

92
00:06:38,148 --> 00:06:39,941
少爷，甚么金鱼、木鱼？
What does that mean?

93
00:06:39,983 --> 00:06:41,776
傻瓜，金鱼只可以看
You idiot! Gold fish is for watching only

94
00:06:41,776 --> 00:06:43,486
木鱼则可以碰嘛
Cooked fish can be eaten

95
00:06:43,862 --> 00:06:45,906
那当然要木鱼
Cooked fish of course

96
00:06:46,114 --> 00:06:48,325
你们还不过来待候客人⋯
You, cooked fish, why don't you come and serve Mr So?

97
00:06:49,242 --> 00:06:51,161
苏翁，今天是你的大日子
Mr So, you are the superior master today

98
00:06:51,369 --> 00:06:53,288
你想要怎样的女人，你说就成
What kind of woman do you want? Just tell me

99
00:06:53,538 --> 00:06:55,749
随便，女人都是一样的
I won't mind, every woman is just the same

100
00:06:55,790 --> 00:06:57,000
没甚么特别
Nothing special

101
00:07:02,255 --> 00:07:04,090
苏翁，甚么事？
Mr So, what's the matter?

102
00:07:04,758 --> 00:07:05,926
我给人挑了一下
I am attacked

103
00:07:05,967 --> 00:07:06,676
甚么？
What?

104
00:07:06,676 --> 00:07:08,386
谁胆敢挑你？让我打她的咀
Who dared so? I will hit that bastard's mouth for you

105
00:07:08,553 --> 00:07:09,137
不是用咀
She didn't use her mouth

106
00:07:09,471 --> 00:07:10,221
是用眼睛
She used her eyes

107
00:07:10,555 --> 00:07:13,934
诱惑中带有煞气，这种眼神我没见过
Tempting, and I smell blood I haven't seen such eyesight before

108
00:07:14,184 --> 00:07:16,019
究竟是何方神圣？
Who is she?

109
00:07:16,394 --> 00:07:18,188
这位如霜姑娘是客串
Miss Yushang comes to be a part-time hooker only

110
00:07:18,438 --> 00:07:20,190
赵大人有没有兴趣和她摆房？
Is Mr Chiu interested to sleep with her?

111
00:07:20,273 --> 00:07:21,691
你应该先问皇爷才对
You should ask His Majesty first

112
00:07:21,983 --> 00:07:23,234
怎么样，皇爷？
How is it? Your Majesty?

113
00:07:23,693 --> 00:07:26,613
大家自己人，何必客气呢？
We are friends, just go ahead if you want!

114
00:07:27,072 --> 00:07:28,573
赵先生，请随便
Mr Chiu, help yourself

115
00:07:29,282 --> 00:07:30,367
那我就却之不恭了
Thank you then

116
00:07:30,742 --> 00:07:31,576
摆房
The room service please

117
00:07:32,369 --> 00:07:35,372
如霜，快点下来见赵大人
Yushang, come and greet Mr Chiu

118
00:07:38,124 --> 00:07:39,042
姐姐，就是他
Sister, he is the one we want

119
00:07:39,292 --> 00:07:40,418
杀阿爹的人就是他
He killed dad

120
00:07:40,919 --> 00:07:41,836
我知道，镇定点
I know, stay calm

121
00:07:41,836 --> 00:07:42,587
走吧
Let's go

122
00:07:43,004 --> 00:07:44,130
失陪　　赵大人
- May I be excused    - Mr Chiu

123
00:07:44,130 --> 00:07:45,715
如霜姑娘到
Miss Yushang has arrived

124
00:07:48,259 --> 00:07:52,097
小女子如霜，拜见赵大人
How are you, Mr Chiu?

125
00:07:56,893 --> 00:07:57,936
果然是美人
A pretty woman!

126
00:07:59,854 --> 00:08:02,565
赵大人，那今晚⋯
Mr Chiu, about tonight…

127
00:08:02,649 --> 00:08:04,067
银票十万两
100,000 taels

128
00:08:04,609 --> 00:08:07,028
如霜姑娘今晚要陪我家少爷
if Miss Yushang sleeps with our young master tonight…

129
00:08:07,237 --> 00:08:08,571
没空招呼你
You are not welcome

130
00:08:08,571 --> 00:08:11,199
各位⋯真不好意思
I am sorry, I am damn sorry

131
00:08:11,491 --> 00:08:12,659
有甚么意见吗？
Don't you have any objection?

132
00:08:13,702 --> 00:08:16,371
让我来⋯让我说句公道话
Let me say something fair

133
00:08:16,621 --> 00:08:19,124
只要你们谁能付超过十万两银票
If any of you can offer more than 100,000 taels

134
00:08:19,290 --> 00:08:20,834
如霜姑娘就陪谁
Yushang will sleep with whom

135
00:08:21,001 --> 00:08:24,004
千万不要伤和气，对不对？
Don't quarrel because of such a small amount, isn't it right?

136
00:08:24,170 --> 00:08:25,880
这位朋友真舍得花钱
Pal, you are a big spender

137
00:08:27,257 --> 00:08:29,134
银票实在太普通
The cheque is too simple to me

138
00:08:30,635 --> 00:08:35,098
我有一颗朝廷大内的定风珠，无价宝
I have a pearl which is granted by the Royal family, it's invaluable!

139
00:08:38,101 --> 00:08:39,853
我还是比较喜欢珍珠
I love the pearl more

140
00:08:41,855 --> 00:08:44,482
赵大人，我回房间等你
Mr Chiu, I will wait for you in my room

141
00:08:45,275 --> 00:08:46,901
这颗珠值十万两吗？
Does the pearl worth 100,000 taels?

142
00:08:47,736 --> 00:08:49,779
十万两你还嫌少吗，姑娘？
Don't you think that's too little for you?

143
00:08:50,071 --> 00:08:53,992
我也喜欢银两，只是不喜欢你
I love money too. But, I don't like you

144
00:08:57,287 --> 00:08:59,873
够坦白，我真的非常喜欢
You are frank! I love it very much

145
00:08:59,914 --> 00:09:00,749
苏翁⋯
Mr So…

146
00:09:00,749 --> 00:09:01,750
没相干
It doesn't matter,

147
00:09:01,791 --> 00:09:03,877
一定是我今天的帽子和发型不配
I think, my hat doesn't match me

148
00:09:03,877 --> 00:09:06,755
如霜姑娘看不上我，是我该死
Yushang doesn't like me, I deserve it

149
00:09:06,796 --> 00:09:08,048
你明白就好了
I am glad you understand this

150
00:09:08,089 --> 00:09:10,341
放心，我还有很多很漂亮的姑娘
Don't worry, I have many pretty girls here

151
00:09:10,341 --> 00:09:13,678
鸨母，那今晚就倚仗你了
I trust your arrangement

152
00:09:16,347 --> 00:09:17,974
这与我无关
None of my business

153
00:09:18,016 --> 00:09:19,642
大胆！放肆
How bold are you?

154
00:09:28,943 --> 00:09:31,112
螳螂拳？像模像样的
Mantis Fist? It seems to be powerful

155
00:09:31,529 --> 00:09:32,238
奏乐
Music!

156
00:09:39,996 --> 00:09:40,872
先放好
Keep this

157
00:09:42,082 --> 00:09:42,791
鹤咀
See my Crane's Fists!

158
00:09:42,791 --> 00:09:43,666
虎爪
The Tiger's Claws!

159
00:09:48,588 --> 00:09:51,841
螳螂怎跟老虎斗？何况我还有一只鹤
How can a mantis fight with a tiger?

160
00:09:52,467 --> 00:09:54,135
虎鹤双形我也会
I know Tiger Claws and Crane's Fists too!

161
00:09:55,470 --> 00:09:57,597
那你试试看我的螳螂
Well, try my mantis!

162
00:10:10,735 --> 00:10:12,695
好⋯好
Bravo…

163
00:10:12,695 --> 00:10:15,573
我的螳螂拳再破你的虎鹤双形
Your Tiger's Claws are defeated

164
00:10:17,325 --> 00:10:18,827
原来不是虎鹤双形
Actually it's not Tiger's Claws,

165
00:10:18,827 --> 00:10:20,203
是孔雀开屏
it's beggar's fists!

166
00:10:20,537 --> 00:10:21,871
难怪比较差
That's why it's too weak

167
00:10:28,128 --> 00:10:29,129
动作蛮快
You move fast!

168
00:10:29,379 --> 00:10:30,880
看来你比较像样
It seems to be powerful…

169
00:10:32,632 --> 00:10:35,802
年青人，不知天高地厚
Kid, you don't know how the wind blows

170
00:10:42,267 --> 00:10:44,185
广州将军到
The general of Canton has arrived

171
00:10:44,227 --> 00:10:45,520
走开⋯
Get lost…

172
00:10:47,272 --> 00:10:49,524
谁敢欺负我的儿子，我就射谁
Who dares bully my son, let me teach him a lesson

173
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:50,900
老爷
Master

174
00:10:51,151 --> 00:10:52,735
不用害怕，阿灿，谁欺负你？
Don't panic, Chan who bullied you?

175
00:10:52,735 --> 00:10:53,486
是我欺负别人
It's me who bullied others

176
00:10:53,528 --> 00:10:55,196
甚么？你欺负别人？
What? You bullied others?

177
00:10:55,488 --> 00:10:57,323
他有多少家财？他够不够资格
How much does he have? Is he qualified to be bullied by you?

178
00:10:57,574 --> 00:10:58,575
老爷！是他们
Master, they are the ones

179
00:10:58,575 --> 00:10:59,284
谁？
Who are they?

180
00:10:59,325 --> 00:11:00,660
你看看就知道
Just take a look

181
00:11:02,996 --> 00:11:04,247
铁帽子王？
The King of Iron Hat?

182
00:11:07,167 --> 00:11:07,959
送贺礼
Send the gift

183
00:11:07,959 --> 00:11:08,459
阿灿
Chan

184
00:11:08,501 --> 00:11:10,753
人家送那么厚的礼就不要再欺负他
They send you such a valuable present, you'd stop bullying them

185
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:12,589
来⋯拿去打赏给这里的姑娘　　老爷
- Come on, give tips to the girl here    - Master

186
00:11:12,630 --> 00:11:15,425
令牌上写著「铁帽子王僧格林参」
King of Iron Hat, Seng-ko-lin-ch'in is written on the medal

187
00:11:25,977 --> 00:11:27,520
你胆敢抢皇爷的令牌？
How dare you seize the medal of His Majesty?

188
00:11:27,770 --> 00:11:28,313
把他锁起来
Cuff him

189
00:11:28,313 --> 00:11:31,065
等一等！根据大清律例
Hold it, according to the Ching's law,

190
00:11:31,399 --> 00:11:33,610
身为朝廷命官，不得嫖妓
Courtier is not allowed hooking

191
00:11:34,027 --> 00:11:35,236
你现在身在怡红院
Now, you are in the brothel

192
00:11:35,445 --> 00:11:37,280
知法犯法，该当何罪？
Do you know you have violated the laws of Ching?

193
00:11:37,780 --> 00:11:38,698
那么你呢？
How about you?

194
00:11:39,157 --> 00:11:40,283
你说我？　　是
- You mean me?    - Yes!

195
00:11:40,283 --> 00:11:42,452
对呀，我是来⋯
That's right, I come…

196
00:11:42,452 --> 00:11:43,286
来拉⋯　　拉你
- to arrest…    - You!

197
00:11:43,286 --> 00:11:44,954
他！　　拉他
- Him!    - Arrest him

198
00:11:45,205 --> 00:11:46,664
我身为广州将军
I am the general of Canton,

199
00:11:46,664 --> 00:11:49,167
当然要来拉你这害群之马
so I should arrest those bad people

200
00:11:49,292 --> 00:11:50,168
还有⋯还有
By the way…

201
00:11:50,168 --> 00:11:52,003
还有甚么？说吧
What else? Go ahead

202
00:11:52,420 --> 00:11:55,590
今天是清太祖皇后叶赫拿拉氏的忌辰
Today is the birthday of the ex-Empress Dowager

203
00:11:56,257 --> 00:11:57,842
身为京官罪加一等
So your crime is doubled

204
00:11:57,842 --> 00:11:58,885
可以问斩
It may lead to capital punishment

205
00:11:58,968 --> 00:12:01,137
斩他⋯斩他
Kill him…

206
00:12:05,725 --> 00:12:06,976
根据大清律例
According to the Ching laws,

207
00:12:07,143 --> 00:12:09,312
任何人不束辫子也要问斩
anyone without a tail should be killed

208
00:12:09,979 --> 00:12:11,147
那你是要⋯
So you…

209
00:12:13,775 --> 00:12:14,776
还想不想看？
Do you want to see my hair?

210
00:12:15,235 --> 00:12:16,361
再多也有，傻瓜
You can see as much as you want! Fat-head

211
00:12:16,402 --> 00:12:18,988
不用再说，斩他
Cut the crap, just kill him

212
00:12:18,988 --> 00:12:21,241
好了好了，玩完了
OK, it's finished

213
00:12:21,366 --> 00:12:23,785
苏将军，大家玩得那么开心就算了吧
General So, let's play happily together, so forget it

214
00:12:24,035 --> 00:12:25,328
我今晚还没玩过
I haven't played!

215
00:12:26,037 --> 00:12:26,496
皇爷
Your Majesty,

216
00:12:26,913 --> 00:12:28,831
没想到在这里会让他们打扰你的雅兴
a rascal has ruined the atmosphere here,

217
00:12:28,998 --> 00:12:30,041
小人安排不周
I should be blamed for poor arrangement

218
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:31,501
这与你无关
None of your business

219
00:12:32,126 --> 00:12:33,211
我们走
Let's go

220
00:12:35,630 --> 00:12:38,883
老爷！这个不能惹，见好就收
Master, you can't fool this guy. Let's go

221
00:12:39,717 --> 00:12:40,510
收吧
OK, go

222
00:12:41,552 --> 00:12:44,138
大事化小，小事化无
Just forget the trouble

223
00:12:46,266 --> 00:12:49,310
少爷，你的帽子
Young master, your hat

224
00:12:55,566 --> 00:12:56,985
真是高手
He is great!

225
00:13:06,077 --> 00:13:09,080
莫大叔，酒菜已经加了断肠散
Uncle Mok, the dishes are all poisoned

226
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:13,167
好！赵无极暗算我们帮主
Chiu assassinated our Master

227
00:13:13,167 --> 00:13:14,919
和太平天国的几名将领
and some generals of The Taiping Reign

228
00:13:15,503 --> 00:13:17,005
还嫁祸给我们丐帮
And he framed us, the Beggars Association, to be the assassins

229
00:13:17,964 --> 00:13:19,340
弄得江湖上的兄弟
Thus made us

230
00:13:19,632 --> 00:13:20,925
人人也瞧不起我们
to be despised by the world

231
00:13:21,718 --> 00:13:23,303
说我们投靠了朝廷
Saying that we became the dogs of the government

232
00:13:23,845 --> 00:13:25,888
这个仇今天可以报了
I should ask him to pay for it

233
00:13:27,557 --> 00:13:29,100
他们的先天罡气很厉害
His initial power is harmful

234
00:13:29,392 --> 00:13:31,561
你们待会见他没上当，千万别出手
Don't take action until he is trapped

235
00:13:31,853 --> 00:13:34,147
因为凑合我们几个也不是他的对手
Because we can't defeat him even if we group together

236
00:13:34,689 --> 00:13:36,316
我会尽量诱他到床边
I will try my best to seduce him to the bed

237
00:13:37,442 --> 00:13:38,860
长老，有人来
Senior, somebody is coming

238
00:13:39,402 --> 00:13:40,445
大家准备⋯
Get ready…

239
00:13:48,911 --> 00:13:50,621
如霜姑娘，我们又见面了
Miss Yushang, we meet again

240
00:13:50,663 --> 00:13:52,665
怎么是你？赵大爷呢？
Why do you come here? Where is Mister Chiu?

241
00:13:52,665 --> 00:13:54,208
赵大爷的定风珠
The pearl of Mr Chiu is broken

242
00:13:54,292 --> 00:13:56,044
给苏翁一打就变成珍珠粉末
by Mr So and became pearl powder

243
00:13:56,044 --> 00:13:57,337
我冲水喝了
I have drunk it

244
00:13:58,212 --> 00:14:00,048
你不要看苏翁的头发像扫帚
Don't judge Mr So from his hair,

245
00:14:00,340 --> 00:14:02,633
其实他为人很有情趣
he is really romantic and funny

246
00:14:03,009 --> 00:14:03,551
但是⋯
But…

247
00:14:03,551 --> 00:14:06,054
但是甚么，十万两我已拿了
Stop, I have taken his money, 100,000 taels you know?

248
00:14:06,262 --> 00:14:07,764
我不会还给他的
I won't give it back

249
00:14:08,306 --> 00:14:09,724
说到苏翁的为人⋯
About the personality of Mr So…

250
00:14:09,807 --> 00:14:11,309
废话少说，鸨母
Cut the crap, pimp!

251
00:14:11,517 --> 00:14:12,310
你先出去
Leave here first

252
00:14:12,310 --> 00:14:13,519
是的⋯是的
Yes, you are right

253
00:14:13,936 --> 00:14:15,938
七姑娘⋯　　将就一下⋯
- Miss Seven…    - Just accept this

254
00:14:20,860 --> 00:14:21,652
这个是谁？
Who is this guy?

255
00:14:22,362 --> 00:14:23,237
我不知道
I don't know

256
00:14:23,488 --> 00:14:26,574
姑娘，首先有个好消息
Miss, first of all, I have good news for you

257
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:28,076
我很喜欢你
I love you

258
00:14:29,202 --> 00:14:31,454
这对我来说是一个坏消息
To me, this is a bad news

259
00:14:31,871 --> 00:14:33,539
我早知道你会这样说
I know you will reply like this

260
00:14:33,956 --> 00:14:34,832
闲话休提
Cut the crap

261
00:14:34,999 --> 00:14:36,209
我愿意出一百颗珍珠
I wish to pay you 100 pearls

262
00:14:36,209 --> 00:14:39,128
希望如霜姑娘今晚能够陪我把酒谈欢
for your company tonight

263
00:14:39,420 --> 00:14:40,505
我不想跟你多说
I don't want to talk to you

264
00:14:40,505 --> 00:14:41,547
请你出去
Please get out

265
00:14:43,383 --> 00:14:44,592
我果然没选错人
I haven't chosen the wrong one

266
00:14:44,759 --> 00:14:46,844
好，我先饮为敬
OK, I will drink this wine first

267
00:14:47,470 --> 00:14:48,346
不要喝⋯
No…

268
00:14:54,727 --> 00:14:56,854
实在让我太感意外
It surprised me

269
00:14:58,022 --> 00:14:58,648
姑娘
Miss

270
00:14:58,940 --> 00:14:59,899
放手
Hands off!

271
00:15:01,859 --> 00:15:03,152
原来你会武功
You know kung fu?

272
00:15:03,986 --> 00:15:05,780
不，我根本就不会武功
No, I don't know Kung-fu at all

273
00:15:06,197 --> 00:15:07,782
我求求你别再缠著我
I beg you, stop bothering me

274
00:15:08,032 --> 00:15:09,033
我不会陪你
I won't accompany you

275
00:15:09,283 --> 00:15:12,161
如霜，从来没有人这样对我
Yushang, no one treats me like this

276
00:15:12,578 --> 00:15:14,372
我发觉我已经爱上了你
I have found that I am in love with you

277
00:15:16,207 --> 00:15:17,083
你说甚么？
What?

278
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:21,212
我说，我已经爱上了你
I have been in love with you

279
00:15:22,213 --> 00:15:23,464
你没有弄错吧？
Are you kidding?

280
00:15:23,923 --> 00:15:26,426
绝对没有！我决定要娶你
I am not kidding, I decided to marry you

281
00:15:27,427 --> 00:15:28,719
你有神经病
Are you nuts?

282
00:15:30,096 --> 00:15:30,972
不是吧
Kidding?

283
00:15:33,891 --> 00:15:35,852
原来有人藏在这里
Is there anyone hiding here?

284
00:15:39,063 --> 00:15:41,065
正好，我正想找个证人
That's good, I want a witness

285
00:15:41,232 --> 00:15:42,567
证人？　　对
- Witness?    - Yes

286
00:15:43,276 --> 00:15:44,861
我就对著你的宝剑发誓
I swear in front of your sword

287
00:15:45,153 --> 00:15:46,904
我是真心要娶如霜姑娘为妻
I do want to marry Miss Yushang as my wife, I am sincere

288
00:15:46,904 --> 00:15:49,157
若然有半句假话，天打雷劈
If I cheat, I will be killed by thunder

289
00:15:50,324 --> 00:15:52,452
姐姐，我真的替你兴奋⋯
Sister, I feel excited for you

290
00:15:52,618 --> 00:15:53,661
唏！
Hey

291
00:15:55,079 --> 00:15:56,706
你以为当我丈夫那么容易吗
Don't you know it isn't that easy to be my husband?

292
00:15:57,039 --> 00:15:58,624
要怎样才可以当你丈夫呢？
How can I be your husband?

293
00:16:00,209 --> 00:16:02,086
我要他武功盖世，状元之才
I want him to be the superior Kung-fu master

294
00:16:02,128 --> 00:16:03,504
一人之下，万人之上
Be the top of all

295
00:16:03,671 --> 00:16:04,839
那你是否做得到？
Can you do that?

296
00:16:05,673 --> 00:16:06,507
让我想一想
Let me think for one second

297
00:16:13,222 --> 00:16:13,931
做得到
I can do it

298
00:16:16,476 --> 00:16:17,059
好
OK

299
00:16:17,101 --> 00:16:19,520
待你做得到的时候，才回来找我
Do it first and then look for me

300
00:16:19,770 --> 00:16:23,399
既然如此，我想我们要先定婚期
Well, I think we should fix a date for our wedding

301
00:16:23,900 --> 00:16:26,694
因为做状元对我来说易如反掌
Because, this is too easy for me to be the Kung-fu scholar!

302
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:30,781
好！那也应该给我时间作考虑
OK, but you'd give me some time to consider it

303
00:16:30,948 --> 00:16:33,701
没问题，我就在外面的花园等待答复
No problem, I will wait for your answer outside the garden

304
00:16:34,452 --> 00:16:35,786
不见不散
I won't leave until seeing you

305
00:16:39,749 --> 00:16:41,459
变态
Crazy!

306
00:17:03,940 --> 00:17:07,276
丐帮办事，闲杂人等立即离开
We come for the Beggars Association, those unrelated persons leave at once

307
00:18:03,833 --> 00:18:06,544
大人，半炷香的时间刚刚好
Sir, the timing is right

308
00:18:07,003 --> 00:18:09,213
现在路上很安全，请上路
The road is safe now, please go

309
00:18:10,590 --> 00:18:13,217
好！非常好
Good, very good

310
00:18:15,386 --> 00:18:16,470
起轿！
Let's go!

311
00:18:28,816 --> 00:18:31,861
糟糕！我们来晚了
Shit, we are late

312
00:18:32,653 --> 00:18:34,363
都是那个人碍事！
That Manchurian should be blamed

313
00:18:41,537 --> 00:18:43,372
姐姐⋯姐姐
Sister…

314
00:18:43,372 --> 00:18:43,914
甚么事？
What's the matter?

315
00:18:44,290 --> 00:18:45,541
那个神经病还在
The idiot is still there

316
00:18:45,875 --> 00:18:46,959
不如杀了他
Let's kill him

317
00:18:47,376 --> 00:18:49,420
算吧！他不是有心阻碍我们
Forget it, he doesn't mean to bother us

318
00:18:50,087 --> 00:18:50,713
由他吧
Let him go

319
00:19:02,892 --> 00:19:04,560
你不是喜欢他吧？
Are you fond of him?

320
00:19:05,061 --> 00:19:06,312
你胡说甚么？
What did you say?

321
00:19:06,562 --> 00:19:07,772
赵无极一日不死
I won't fall in love with anybody

322
00:19:07,980 --> 00:19:09,649
我也不会想这些事
until Chiu is killed

323
00:19:10,066 --> 00:19:11,067
何况是他
Especially him

324
00:19:11,901 --> 00:19:13,778
赵无极武功很高
Chiu is good at Kung-fu

325
00:19:14,070 --> 00:19:17,031
莫大叔说不会降龙十八掌便打不过他
Mok said, we can't defeat him unless using the “Dragon Killing Palms”

326
00:19:17,990 --> 00:19:19,617
那我岂不是嫁不出吗？
So, I can never marry!

327
00:19:20,159 --> 00:19:22,244
行吧！别发情
Let's go, if you want to marry

328
00:19:40,680 --> 00:19:42,848
何方妖孽？竟敢来嚇我？
What evil are you? How dare you scare me?

329
00:19:43,683 --> 00:19:47,228
苏翁，我是鸨母⋯
Mr So, it's me!

330
00:19:48,979 --> 00:19:49,814
你是鸨母？
You are the pimp?!

331
00:19:49,939 --> 00:19:50,940
是的
Yes!

332
00:19:51,023 --> 00:19:52,733
胸部那么平，你的奶子呢？
You have a flat figure, where are your busts?

333
00:19:52,858 --> 00:19:55,903
那么早，还未睡醒⋯
It's early in the morning, they haven't woken up yet

334
00:19:56,237 --> 00:19:57,780
这次没有把你打死，算是你走运
It's lucky of you for not being killed

335
00:19:57,947 --> 00:19:59,615
以后没有化粧不要四处走，知道吗？
Don't go around if you haven't made up yet

336
00:19:59,615 --> 00:20:01,158
不会了，不会了
I won't do it again

337
00:20:01,575 --> 00:20:05,746
你不用等如霜姑娘了，她已经走了⋯
Stop waiting for Miss Yushang, she left

338
00:20:06,247 --> 00:20:07,081
走了？
What?

339
00:20:11,168 --> 00:20:12,962
那究竟如霜姑娘去了哪里？
Where is she going?

340
00:20:13,587 --> 00:20:17,675
听说，她⋯她去了京城
She… she is going to Peking

341
00:20:18,134 --> 00:20:19,093
京城？
Peking?

342
00:20:19,885 --> 00:20:24,557
男儿为国家⋯
Men should contribute to the country

343
00:20:24,890 --> 00:20:28,644
⋯辫子怎样戴⋯
Where should I put my pigtail?

344
00:20:28,811 --> 00:20:30,730
挥啊！挥啊！
Swing and swing…

345
00:20:30,938 --> 00:20:32,773
我拉长它又弹它⋯
I pull it and play it…

346
00:20:33,357 --> 00:20:34,233
阿爹
Dad!

347
00:20:34,942 --> 00:20:36,485
我决定上京考文武状元
I decided to join the examination for the Scholar of Martial Arts

348
00:20:37,194 --> 00:20:38,154
阿灿
Chan

349
00:20:38,863 --> 00:20:40,740
爹等你说这句话，等了二十五年
I have been longing for this word for 25 years

350
00:20:40,740 --> 00:20:42,867
为了苏察哈尔家，你应该这样做
For the sake of our family, you should do that

351
00:20:42,908 --> 00:20:44,869
别误会，我这样做并不是为谁
Don't misunderstand it, I do it not for no one

352
00:20:44,869 --> 00:20:45,619
只是为了一个女人
But for a woman

353
00:20:45,870 --> 00:20:46,787
英雄
What a hero!

354
00:20:47,371 --> 00:20:49,665
为妞死，为妞亡，为妞上京考状元
For a girl, you want to be the Scholar of Martial Arts!

355
00:20:49,665 --> 00:20:50,583
何家女子？
Who is that girl?

356
00:20:50,624 --> 00:20:53,127
怡红院金牌清官人如霜姑娘
The hooker of Yee Hung Brothel, Miss Yushang

357
00:20:53,294 --> 00:20:54,503
妓女？
For a hooker?

358
00:20:55,755 --> 00:20:56,547
有何不妥？
What's wrong with it?

359
00:20:57,757 --> 00:21:00,384
品味与别不同，真是能人所不能
You have different taste, you are great!

360
00:21:00,509 --> 00:21:01,510
阿爹钦佩你
I am admiring you!

361
00:21:01,510 --> 00:21:02,470
我陪你上京
I will accompany you to Peking

362
00:21:02,845 --> 00:21:04,013
二，三，四，五，六
2, 3, 4, 5, 6

363
00:21:04,054 --> 00:21:06,474
来了，老爷
I am coming

364
00:21:06,515 --> 00:21:09,059
少爷上京赴考，我们搬家
Young master is going for the examination, let's move to Peking too

365
00:21:10,895 --> 00:21:12,646
你们不要追了
Stop chasing,

366
00:21:12,688 --> 00:21:15,107
这些鸡不带了，京城多的是
we won't take the hens with us

367
00:21:16,192 --> 00:21:18,319
你这个笨蛋小心点
Be careful!

368
00:21:18,319 --> 00:21:21,030
弄花了我的东西，我不会放过你
If you break my stuff, I will teach you a good lesson

369
00:21:21,280 --> 00:21:22,573
小心点
Be careful!

370
00:21:23,491 --> 00:21:24,116
老爹，早
Good morning Dad

371
00:21:24,283 --> 00:21:24,909
早
Good morning

372
00:21:24,909 --> 00:21:25,868
真的全部都搬走？
You want to move everything to Peking?

373
00:21:25,868 --> 00:21:26,702
当然
Sure

374
00:21:26,827 --> 00:21:28,537
留件衣服给我穿啊
Please leave me a cloth

375
00:21:28,579 --> 00:21:30,498
小孩子怕甚么呢？
You are only a kid, you don't need this

376
00:21:30,581 --> 00:21:31,957
我不小了
But I am not small

377
00:21:33,167 --> 00:21:35,669
呸！比我大吗？
Are you bigger than mine?

378
00:21:35,836 --> 00:21:36,587
小看我？
You despise me!

