573
00:39:41,921 --> 00:39:43,506
谢皇上
Thank you

574
00:39:44,966 --> 00:39:47,927
僧格林参，今科武状元是谁？
Who is the new Scholar of Martial Arts?

575
00:39:50,179 --> 00:39:53,516
禀告皇上，是广东的苏察哈尔灿
Your Majesty, So Chan from Canton is the Scholar this year

576
00:39:56,436 --> 00:39:58,813
苏察哈尔灿！参见皇上
Your Majesty, I am So Cha Ha Yee Chan

577
00:40:00,940 --> 00:40:03,067
皇上，微臣有事启奏
Your Majesty, I want to report something

578
00:40:05,653 --> 00:40:06,404
准奏
Go ahead

579
00:40:08,281 --> 00:40:10,491
微臣查出苏察哈尔灿目不识丁
I have found that So is illiterate

580
00:40:10,783 --> 00:40:12,410
怎可以答到考战略的题目呢？
So how could he answer the question paper of strategy?

581
00:40:12,577 --> 00:40:13,536
分明有诈
That should be a trick

582
00:40:18,166 --> 00:40:19,417
给朕拿文房四宝来
Take the stationery out!

583
00:40:19,417 --> 00:40:20,418
是
Yes

584
00:40:25,214 --> 00:40:28,509
苏察哈尔灿，马上写出你的名字来
So Cha Ha Yee Chan, write your name now

585
00:40:30,136 --> 00:40:33,097
走运了！他懂得写名字
Thank God, he knows how to write his name!

586
00:40:33,348 --> 00:40:35,141
懂写名字！懂写名字
He can write his name!

587
00:40:48,154 --> 00:40:48,905
我不会写
I don't know how to write

588
00:40:51,074 --> 00:40:52,075
你分明作弊
That's shit!

589
00:40:52,992 --> 00:40:53,910
拉他出去斩
Kill him now

590
00:40:54,994 --> 00:40:56,204
不要！不要
No! No!

591
00:40:57,997 --> 00:40:59,624
皇上，作弊的是奴才
Your Majesty, I am the one who cheated

592
00:40:59,624 --> 00:41:00,583
不关我儿子的事
It's none of his business

593
00:41:00,625 --> 00:41:01,459
要斩就斩我吧
Just chop me to death

594
00:41:01,459 --> 00:41:02,710
不对！应该斩我
No, you should kill me

595
00:41:02,710 --> 00:41:03,544
对不起，阿爹
Sorry dad

596
00:41:03,586 --> 00:41:04,879
其实我连自己名字都不会写
I don't know how to write my name

597
00:41:04,879 --> 00:41:06,255
不用说！刚刚知道了
Stop, I have known it already

598
00:41:06,547 --> 00:41:07,590
皇上！要斩就斩我吧
Your Majesty, I should be killed

599
00:41:07,590 --> 00:41:08,758
斩我吧　　斩我吧
- Kill me    - No, kill me

600
00:41:08,800 --> 00:41:10,677
斩我吧　　皇上！你还是斩我吧
- Kill me.    - Your Majesty, you'd better kill me

601
00:41:10,718 --> 00:41:12,971
混帐！你们说要斩谁就斩谁吗
Shit, are you giving order?

602
00:41:13,554 --> 00:41:14,973
你两父子同谋
You two cooperated to cheat me

603
00:41:15,390 --> 00:41:17,308
吏部尚书按例判刑
The Secretary for Justice, announce the penalty for them

604
00:41:18,434 --> 00:41:21,562
吏部尚书，快点出来！出来
Come out! Hurry up

605
00:41:21,688 --> 00:41:23,815
我在这里！在这里
I am here!

606
00:41:27,694 --> 00:41:29,028
他是吏部尚书？
He is the Secretary for Justice

607
00:41:29,529 --> 00:41:33,533
苏察哈尔灿两父子罪犯欺君理应问斩
So's family should be sentenced to death

608
00:41:35,368 --> 00:41:38,121
念在你是功臣之后！可免一死
But their ancestors achieved a lot for Ching, they can be exempted

609
00:41:38,329 --> 00:41:41,541
但贪赃依例充公，枉法吗⋯
But, their fortune should be forfeited

610
00:41:42,125 --> 00:41:43,209
你有没有执过法？
Have you carried out any military duty?

611
00:41:43,668 --> 00:41:46,295
没有！我七年都没有到过军营
I haven't gone back to my camp for 7 years, I haven't done anything

612
00:41:47,463 --> 00:41:50,049
没有执法即是没有枉法
So, he didn't miscarry out any duty

613
00:41:51,300 --> 00:41:52,635
是这样的
So, the maximum penalty

614
00:41:52,927 --> 00:41:55,096
皇上，依例最多判抄家的罪
is forfeiture of property only

615
00:41:58,558 --> 00:42:00,643
这么轻？你有没有记错？
What? Are you sure?

616
00:42:01,561 --> 00:42:02,812
奴才很公正的
I am fair

617
00:42:02,895 --> 00:42:05,440
全都是依足基本法例办事
I judge it from the Law Book

618
00:42:06,691 --> 00:42:08,443
那朕现在多加刑罚行不行？
Can I add something?

619
00:42:09,193 --> 00:42:11,988
皇上说要加，当然没问题
Sure, since you are the Emperor

620
00:42:12,113 --> 00:42:14,907
好！那朕就判你们两父子一辈子讨饭
I want them to be beggars for the rest of their lives

621
00:42:15,324 --> 00:42:16,367
僧格林参
Why couldn't you find out

622
00:42:16,451 --> 00:42:17,744
为甚么他作弊你没有查出来
they cheated during the examination?

623
00:42:18,077 --> 00:42:19,537
这一次幸好有赵无极
Luckily Chiu reported it to me on time

624
00:42:19,787 --> 00:42:22,832
赵无极，你揭发有功！朕会好好赏你
Chiu, you would be rewarded

625
00:42:24,834 --> 00:42:28,963
身如柳絮⋯
I am wandering…

626
00:42:29,380 --> 00:42:32,133
这是我爹的神主牌位，你也要没收
That's the spirit tablet of my dad, do you want to take it too?

627
00:42:33,301 --> 00:42:35,219
这个香炉锅，你拿了也没用
It's useless for you

628
00:42:35,303 --> 00:42:45,438
⋯历劫沧桑⋯鸳鸯扣
How poor are we…

629
00:42:45,688 --> 00:42:52,028
宜结不宜解，苦相思⋯
I am thinking of my better half…

630
00:42:52,028 --> 00:42:53,112
少爷
Young master,

631
00:42:54,072 --> 00:42:55,406
从今天开始
from now on,

632
00:42:55,448 --> 00:42:57,158
我想你要认真的学写字了
you'd be hardworking to learn how to write

633
00:43:00,912 --> 00:43:08,044
苦相思，能买不能卖⋯
But I can't sell the affection…

634
00:43:11,547 --> 00:43:12,465
师爷
Professor

635
00:43:13,758 --> 00:43:14,717
我会学的
I will learn it

636
00:43:15,885 --> 00:43:21,224
悔不该，惹下⋯
I regret that…

637
00:43:21,224 --> 00:43:24,185
老爷，我会好好把小乌龟养大
Master, I will take good care of the little turtle

638
00:43:24,227 --> 00:43:25,520
对不起，老爷
I am sorry

639
00:43:25,520 --> 00:43:28,147
我们跟你一起这么久，蛋都没有生过
We haven't given birth to any baby of yours

640
00:43:28,189 --> 00:43:29,273
不相干，不相干
It doesn't matter

641
00:43:29,440 --> 00:43:31,526
是老爷办事不力
It's all my fault

642
00:43:31,567 --> 00:43:34,237
若然老爷要的话，孩子多的是了
If I did better, you could have many babies

643
00:43:34,237 --> 00:43:37,073
不过老爷有阿灿一个就够了
But I think Chan is enough for me

644
00:43:38,491 --> 00:43:39,867
还在这干吗？快走
Why are you standing here? Go now

645
00:43:39,867 --> 00:43:41,327
老爷，我们走了
Master, we are leaving

646
00:43:41,327 --> 00:43:42,537
我们走了，老爷
We are leaving, master

647
00:43:42,537 --> 00:43:43,663
走吧，走吧
Go, go now

648
00:43:46,582 --> 00:43:47,792
安乐了
We are free

649
00:43:48,084 --> 00:43:48,793
真开心
I feel so happy

650
00:43:48,793 --> 00:43:50,044
太开心了
How happy are we!

651
00:43:54,757 --> 00:43:56,050
进去，进去
Go in…

652
00:43:56,050 --> 00:43:57,176
快点⋯
Hurry up…

653
00:43:58,553 --> 00:44:01,430
为甚么他们给人家抄家还这样开心？
Why are they so happy?

654
00:44:02,140 --> 00:44:04,725
笑死人了⋯
I am very happy

655
00:44:05,351 --> 00:44:06,352
请进，请进⋯
Please go in…

656
00:44:06,352 --> 00:44:07,478
欢迎⋯欢迎
Welcome…

657
00:44:08,437 --> 00:44:11,524
孩儿，我们被抄家，我很想哭
Damn sequestration, I wanna cry, my son

658
00:44:11,524 --> 00:44:13,693
不要！千万别丢脸
Hold it, don't lose our face

659
00:44:13,734 --> 00:44:14,610
继续笑
Keep on laughing

660
00:44:16,487 --> 00:44:20,116
孩儿，你刚才有没有留点银票傍身
Son. Have you kept any money?

661
00:44:20,116 --> 00:44:21,159
没有！你呢？
No, how about you?

662
00:44:21,409 --> 00:44:23,119
我忘记了
I forgot that

663
00:44:25,580 --> 00:44:29,292
完蛋了！我俩真是完蛋了
Shit, damn sequestration!

664
00:44:30,501 --> 00:44:35,756
善有善报，可怜我这个小乞丐⋯
Be merciful, please give money to us

665
00:44:35,756 --> 00:44:38,759
孩儿！你看这个像不像阿爹？
Son, that guy is like dad

666
00:44:39,177 --> 00:44:40,803
你指唱歌那个？
You mean the one who sings?

667
00:44:40,845 --> 00:44:42,555
不是，是给钱的那个
No, the one who pays

668
00:44:42,597 --> 00:44:45,183
他比唱歌那个更没良心
He is more disgusting than the one who sings

669
00:44:45,183 --> 00:44:48,060
不是吧！多潇洒，各人眼光不同吧
Not exactly, he is smart

670
00:44:48,352 --> 00:44:50,521
都怪老爹不好
Dad should be blamed

671
00:44:50,521 --> 00:44:52,648
以前老叫你小乞丐！小乞丐
I always called you beggar

672
00:44:52,690 --> 00:44:53,608
现在就真的要做了
Now, it becomes true

673
00:44:53,649 --> 00:44:54,692
我并不相信这命运
What's wrong with you?

674
00:44:54,859 --> 00:44:56,152
皇帝要我们做乞丐
The emperor wants us to be beggars

675
00:44:56,152 --> 00:44:57,737
我们就乖乖当乞丐吗？
Do you think we'd be beggars?

676
00:44:58,154 --> 00:44:59,864
以我这种人才和武艺
I am smart, I am keen in kung-fu fighting

677
00:45:00,156 --> 00:45:01,616
天也不准我去当乞丐
Even the Gods won't let me be a beggar

678
00:45:01,866 --> 00:45:02,658
这就是嘛
That's true

679
00:45:02,658 --> 00:45:03,534
我那里像乞丐？
Am I like a beggar?

680
00:45:03,576 --> 00:45:04,327
不像
No

681
00:45:04,535 --> 00:45:06,829
小乞丐老乞丐，拿去买东西吧
Buy something to eat, you beggars

682
00:45:10,166 --> 00:45:11,417
你真的当我们是乞丐？
You treat us as beggars?

683
00:45:11,667 --> 00:45:13,127
混你的帐！你⋯
Damn you!

684
00:45:13,169 --> 00:45:15,963
太过分了！吃饭吃饭
It's weird! Let's eat

685
00:45:19,133 --> 00:45:21,469
阿灿，反正吃饱没事干
Chan, since we have nothing to do

686
00:45:21,510 --> 00:45:24,222
让我在那边坐一会，说不定有晚饭吃
Let me take a seat, maybe we can have something to eat tonight

687
00:45:24,222 --> 00:45:25,723
那你真的当自己是乞丐吗
You are treating yourself a beggar?

688
00:45:26,140 --> 00:45:27,391
阿爹！不用担心
Dad, don't worry

689
00:45:27,642 --> 00:45:29,185
想要钱都不需要去讨
I need no begging for money

690
00:45:29,268 --> 00:45:30,436
不需要讨那里有钱呢？
How can you get money if you don't beg?

691
00:45:30,603 --> 00:45:31,479
问人家借就行了
Just ask someone to give us money

692
00:45:31,479 --> 00:45:33,397
兄弟，贵姓大名？
Pal, may I know your name?

693
00:45:34,398 --> 00:45:35,024
牛大春
Nau Tai Chung

694
00:45:35,274 --> 00:45:36,525
你身上有没有银两？
Do you have money?

695
00:45:36,901 --> 00:45:38,152
有　　借来用用
- Yes    - Just give it to me

696
00:45:38,194 --> 00:45:38,903
好的
OK

697
00:45:43,532 --> 00:45:44,283
多谢
Thank you

698
00:45:45,534 --> 00:45:46,410
我为甚么要给你钱？
Why should I give you money?

699
00:45:47,036 --> 00:45:48,120
你问这么多干甚么！
Why do you ask so many questions?

700
00:45:48,287 --> 00:45:49,622
那总该知道吧
But I should know the reason

701
00:45:49,914 --> 00:45:52,083
知道要给，不知道也要给
Anyway, you should pay it

702
00:45:52,250 --> 00:45:54,210
不行不行，还是弄清楚比较好
No, let's fix it up first

703
00:45:56,295 --> 00:45:57,630
你拿来吧！问这么多干吗
Just give it to us, why are you asking so much?

704
00:45:57,630 --> 00:45:58,631
放手
Hands off

705
00:45:58,673 --> 00:45:59,423
你这样即是抢
You mean robbing?

706
00:45:59,423 --> 00:46:01,884
强盗⋯
Robbery…

707
00:46:01,926 --> 00:46:04,428
不是抢！我们是讨饭
I am not robbing, I am begging

708
00:46:05,429 --> 00:46:07,974
原来你这两个臭东西的想骗我
Begging? How dare you, you beggar, you are cheating me!

709
00:46:07,974 --> 00:46:10,977
别当我呆子！我很聪明的！
Don't you think I am stupid? I am smart, you know?

710
00:46:10,977 --> 00:46:12,103
已两天了
Hey, two days passed,

711
00:46:12,144 --> 00:46:14,272
天气越来越冷！肚子越来越饿
It's cold and I am hungry now

712
00:46:14,272 --> 00:46:15,940
你想到没有？
Have you had any idea?

713
00:46:16,107 --> 00:46:18,901
有办法，我有个朋友的阿姨的妹妹
I have a friend's girlfriend

714
00:46:18,901 --> 00:46:20,194
正好住在京城
who is living in Peking

715
00:46:21,070 --> 00:46:23,322
他早就向我透露很欣赏你
She always admires you

716
00:46:23,489 --> 00:46:24,240
会有这回事？
Really?

717
00:46:24,240 --> 00:46:27,201
是！如果你肯跟他交际一下
Yes, if you are willing to date her

718
00:46:27,451 --> 00:46:29,745
我想他会帮我们忙先回广州
I think she will help us to go back to Canton

719
00:46:30,788 --> 00:46:32,331
但是就要你老人家牺牲一下
But, you have to sacrifice

720
00:46:32,331 --> 00:46:34,166
不知道你老人家意思⋯
Do you mean…

721
00:46:34,417 --> 00:46:36,585
为了这个家，我甚么都可以做
For our family, just as you said

722
00:46:37,044 --> 00:46:37,962
我知道太为难你了
I know it's very hard for you

723
00:46:37,962 --> 00:46:39,255
别再说了！我们去见他
Cut the crap, let's go and find her

724
00:46:39,297 --> 00:46:40,756
我早就跟你安排好了
I have arranged it

725
00:46:41,173 --> 00:46:44,010
就在对面灯笼下穿红衣服的那个
The one wearing red dress who stands under the lantern, that's her

726
00:46:49,515 --> 00:46:51,475
鬼
Ghost!

727
00:46:56,105 --> 00:46:57,023
没问题吗
It's a benefit for you!

728
00:46:57,064 --> 00:46:59,608
没问题！不过你先来，我跟在后面
Why don't you go yourself?

729
00:47:13,581 --> 00:47:15,541
阿灿，胸口碎大石我还没玩过
Chan, I haven't tried this before

730
00:47:15,583 --> 00:47:16,542
小心点
Be careful!

731
00:47:16,542 --> 00:47:17,752
不用怕，我会很小心
Don't worry

732
00:47:17,752 --> 00:47:18,544
确保你没有事
I'll take care of you

733
00:47:18,711 --> 00:47:20,463
你也想赚点钱吃碗鱼翅吧？
You want to earn money for shark-fins, right?

734
00:47:20,463 --> 00:47:21,339
对⋯
Right…

735
00:47:23,424 --> 00:47:26,385
走开⋯走开
Get lost…

736
00:47:26,761 --> 00:47:27,803
不许在这儿卖艺
No show here

737
00:47:31,349 --> 00:47:33,434
大人，我们只想赚点钱
We just want to earn some money

738
00:47:33,434 --> 00:47:34,477
回广州去
to go back to Canton

739
00:47:35,061 --> 00:47:37,521
给我们一条生路，不要赶尽杀绝
Don't be that mean to us

740
00:47:39,690 --> 00:47:40,775
皇上御旨
It's the Royal instruction that

741
00:47:41,025 --> 00:47:43,486
苏察哈尔灿两父子终身行乞
the So's family'd be beggars for life

742
00:47:44,278 --> 00:47:45,780
你们只可以当乞丐
You two can only be beggars

743
00:47:46,155 --> 00:47:48,282
我是奉本子办事！人来
I am carrying out my duty only, men!

744
00:47:48,491 --> 00:47:49,742
有　　将所有东西搬走
- Yes!    - Remove all the things

745
00:47:49,950 --> 00:47:50,659
是
Yes

746
00:47:53,662 --> 00:47:54,872
救命
Help!

747
00:47:55,164 --> 00:47:57,333
赵大人！一个人搬不动
Master Chiu, it's hard for one to carry it

748
00:47:58,042 --> 00:48:00,086
一个搬不动多上几个人
Ask more men to remove it

749
00:48:00,086 --> 00:48:01,462
是
Yes

750
00:48:03,381 --> 00:48:04,131
你们想怎么样？
What do you want?

751
00:48:04,173 --> 00:48:05,800
不行，都搬不动　　让我来吧
- No, we can't move it    - Let me do it

752
00:48:05,841 --> 00:48:07,176
那你是想打架吧？
You want a fight, don't you?

753
00:48:08,260 --> 00:48:10,012
上次你在怡红院逃过一次
Last time you escaped from Yee Hung Hostel

754
00:48:10,471 --> 00:48:11,847
这次你没有这胜券
But you won't be that lucky this time

755
00:48:14,392 --> 00:48:15,643
这个人非同小可
He is powerful!

756
00:48:15,851 --> 00:48:18,354
我一定要在第一招出尽力打败他
I've got to defeat him by one powerful strike

757
00:48:18,854 --> 00:48:20,439
不然他就会有还击的机会
I can't give him another chance to counterattack

758
00:48:42,503 --> 00:48:44,547
阿灿⋯
Chan…

759
00:48:45,339 --> 00:48:48,259
阿灿
Chan…

760
00:48:48,634 --> 00:48:51,804
你的手脚跟全身经脉都给我打断
Your legs and hands are all broken by me

761
00:48:52,596 --> 00:48:54,640
你一辈子都像废人一样！
You will be a cripple for the rest of your life

762
00:48:56,559 --> 00:48:59,103
想用武功？没你份儿！
You want to fight? Not now!

763
00:48:59,770 --> 00:49:02,940
不过，伸手讨几个钱还可以
But, you can beg for money

764
00:49:03,482 --> 00:49:04,650
乖乖当乞丐吧
Be a good beggar

765
00:49:06,610 --> 00:49:10,531
走⋯没事⋯走开
Go, go away…

766
00:49:18,873 --> 00:49:22,668
不用怕阿灿，没事的，没事的⋯
Don't panic, Chan, it's OK

767
00:49:23,377 --> 00:49:28,048
不用怕，没事的⋯
Don't panic, you'll be alright… Chan!

768
00:49:28,257 --> 00:49:30,134
不用怕
Don't panic

769
00:49:31,093 --> 00:49:34,638
那天我跟我儿子踏入试场
I went to the examination hall

770
00:49:34,930 --> 00:49:36,640
再抬头一看那个试官
with my son,

771
00:49:37,057 --> 00:49:38,809
你们猜他是谁？
don't you know who was the examiner?

772
00:49:39,268 --> 00:49:41,729
就是僧格林参这个龟儿子
He is Seng-ko-lin-ch'in, that bastard

773
00:49:42,271 --> 00:49:44,940
这个龟儿子跟我们父子俩有过节吗
He was the enemy of us!

774
00:49:45,357 --> 00:49:46,817
一说到他我就气死了⋯
About our story…

775
00:49:46,817 --> 00:49:48,319
不要说了，先吸口烟
Let me stop here first, I want a smoke

776
00:49:49,612 --> 00:49:51,530
吸口烟提提神
It's better to smoke now

777
00:49:51,572 --> 00:49:53,616
是的，好多了
Yes, it's better

778
00:49:53,699 --> 00:49:57,077
这个王八蛋当日在怡红院
We let him go in

779
00:49:57,286 --> 00:49:59,079
我们父子俩放他一马
the Yee Hung Brothel

780
00:49:59,330 --> 00:50:01,040
想不到他恩将仇报
But he framed us in return

781
00:50:01,540 --> 00:50:03,209
陷害我的儿子
He tricked my son

782
00:50:03,501 --> 00:50:05,669
在兵器上全都动了手脚
during the examination

783
00:50:06,045 --> 00:50:09,173
还好我儿子有真材实料⋯
But, my son was really smart and great

784
00:50:09,256 --> 00:50:11,509
我要他武功盖世，状元之才
To be the greatest Kung-fu fighter, invincible

785
00:50:11,550 --> 00:50:13,844
一人之下，万人之上
Be the top

786
00:50:14,261 --> 00:50:15,596
那你做不做得到呢？
Can you do that?

787
00:50:15,721 --> 00:50:16,430
做得到
Sure!

788
00:50:16,722 --> 00:50:17,389
好
Well

789
00:50:18,098 --> 00:50:20,851
待你做得到的时候就回来找我
Come back to me if you can do that

790
00:50:22,603 --> 00:50:24,188
既然如此，我想我们要先定婚期
I think we should fix our wedding date first

791
00:50:24,563 --> 00:50:27,316
因为做状元对我来说易如反掌
Because being the scholar is too simple for me

792
00:50:36,867 --> 00:50:38,118
马上写出你的名字来
Write your name at once

793
00:50:40,996 --> 00:50:42,122
我不会写
I don't know how to write

794
00:50:52,424 --> 00:50:55,302
灿！怎么？
Chan, what's wrong with you?

795
00:50:58,430 --> 00:50:59,640
又作恶梦？
Nightmare again?

796
00:51:01,183 --> 00:51:02,393
别想这么多
Don't think so much!

797
00:51:09,275 --> 00:51:12,403
虽然休息了两个月，手脚可以动了
Although you have taken 2 months' rest,

798
00:51:13,070 --> 00:51:14,196
但是还没有完全好了
your legs and hands have not been totally recovered

799
00:51:14,196 --> 00:51:17,116
哈尔叔　　来⋯
- Mr. Ha Yee    - Coming

800
00:51:17,741 --> 00:51:20,244
阿爹出去找点食物回来
I am going to beg for food

801
00:51:20,536 --> 00:51:22,830
然后煮最后一趟药给你喝
I will make the last herbal tea for you later

802
00:51:23,581 --> 00:51:25,416
爹，又去讨饭
Dad, you go begging again?

803
00:51:26,166 --> 00:51:28,085
讨饭当然要老夫出马
This job should be left to me

804
00:51:28,127 --> 00:51:29,837
难道要你堂堂武状元⋯
You are the Scholar…

805
00:51:32,256 --> 00:51:36,176
阿灿，原来当乞丐也不简单
Chan, to be a beggar,

806
00:51:36,468 --> 00:51:38,095
有很多窍门
there are some lessons!

807
00:51:38,887 --> 00:51:41,015
不是伸手出来就有钱的
You can't just show your hand and beg for money

808
00:51:41,265 --> 00:51:43,934
至少要拿个砵子！这样才有身份
At least you should have a bowl, that represents your class

809
00:51:43,976 --> 00:51:46,437
乞丐也论身份，真混帐
Is it ridiculous?

810
00:51:47,062 --> 00:51:48,522
快点走
Hurry up

811
00:51:49,982 --> 00:51:52,067
来了
I am coming

812
00:51:52,067 --> 00:51:54,028
再不去就讨不到饭了
We can't beg for food if we are late!

813
00:51:54,028 --> 00:51:54,987
是的⋯
Yes…

814
00:51:55,029 --> 00:51:56,905
你以为自己是以前的大将军
You're not a master now.

815
00:52:14,965 --> 00:52:15,674
给我点钱
Give me money please

816
00:52:15,716 --> 00:52:18,218
没有没有，走吧
Go, go, I won't give you money

817
00:52:18,469 --> 00:52:20,929
走，快走⋯别碍我做生意
Go, don't stop me from doing business

818
00:52:23,891 --> 00:52:25,517
阿灿，阿爹出去了
Chan, dad is leaving

819
00:52:37,821 --> 00:52:41,575
谢谢⋯
Thank you…

820
00:52:47,498 --> 00:52:50,125
谢谢⋯谢谢
Thank you…

821
00:52:56,382 --> 00:52:57,883
别那么吝啬吧，老兄？
Are you that mean?

822
00:52:57,925 --> 00:52:59,009
你不会自己写？
Why don't you write it yourself?

823
00:52:59,093 --> 00:53:01,887
我见你下班了，借你地方用一下吧
You are off duty, so I just want to lend it

824
00:53:02,846 --> 00:53:03,806
你当我呆子吗？
Don't you think I am an idiot?

825
00:53:38,674 --> 00:53:39,633
阿爹
Dad!

826
00:53:41,552 --> 00:53:42,428
你甚么？
What are you doing?

827
00:53:42,803 --> 00:53:46,473
好冷⋯阿灿！好冷⋯
I am cold… I am cold… Chan

828
00:53:48,058 --> 00:53:52,062
好冷？糟糕了！你身体好熨
No, your body is as hot as fire

829
00:53:52,646 --> 00:53:53,480
你病了？
Are you sick?

830
00:53:53,480 --> 00:53:55,149
没有⋯没有
I am not…

831
00:53:56,650 --> 00:53:57,651
这么晚了
It's late

832
00:53:58,527 --> 00:54:00,362
阿爹出去讨些东西给你吃
I have to search for food

833
00:54:02,156 --> 00:54:04,533
你快躺下吧，今天让我去
Lie down, I will go this time

834
00:54:05,159 --> 00:54:06,243
你去讨饭？
Are you going for begging?

835
00:54:06,827 --> 00:54:08,620
没有问题，我会有办法
I have my own way to get food

836
00:54:08,871 --> 00:54:09,705
你休息一下
Take a rest now

837
00:54:10,164 --> 00:54:11,957
我找到钱就回来带你看大夫
I will take you to the doctor after getting some money

838
00:54:31,059 --> 00:54:33,020
你这浑小子为何不吃
You bastard, why don't you eat?

839
00:54:33,020 --> 00:54:35,355
你不吃又怎能像阿爹般强壮
You should eat more so as to be strong!

840
00:54:38,150 --> 00:54:39,276
快点吃
Finish it

841
00:54:39,401 --> 00:54:40,652
吃不下了，我饱了
No, I am full

842
00:54:40,694 --> 00:54:43,238
饱⋯饱也要吃，快点吃
You should take all the food

843
00:54:43,822 --> 00:54:46,450
不吃吗！不吃就回家
OK, just forget it, let's go home

844
00:54:47,242 --> 00:54:50,871
吃！快点吃，吃
Come on, eat them all

845
00:54:53,707 --> 00:54:54,541
小朋友
Little kid!

846
00:54:54,625 --> 00:54:55,167
甚么？
What?

847
00:54:55,167 --> 00:54:57,169
可不可以⋯　　不可以
- May I…    - No

848
00:55:15,395 --> 00:55:22,152
好心吧！福心吧！
Be merciful!

849
00:55:24,154 --> 00:55:29,701
可怜我这个⋯小乞丐
Be merciful to me, please

850
00:55:31,370 --> 00:55:33,831
我爹快要冷死了
My dad is dying!

851
00:55:35,541 --> 00:55:37,501
小乞丐，这里有点碎碳你要不要
Beggar, do you want the broken charcoal?

852
00:55:38,252 --> 00:55:38,961
多谢
Thank you

853
00:55:39,795 --> 00:55:41,630
可不可以再给我多一点零钱
Can you give me some coins?

854
00:55:43,674 --> 00:55:44,633
是你
It's you!

855
00:55:44,758 --> 00:55:45,342
不是我
No, you are mistaken

856
00:55:46,051 --> 00:55:47,678
姐姐！是他
Sister, it's him

857
00:55:47,886 --> 00:55:48,887
不是他！不是他
No, no

858
00:55:48,929 --> 00:55:50,931
姐姐⋯姐姐！苏灿
Sister, he is So Chan

859
00:55:54,309 --> 00:55:55,185
等一下
Wait!

860
00:55:59,815 --> 00:56:01,775
小姐，你找谁呀？
Miss, who are you looking for?

861
00:56:04,486 --> 00:56:05,737
对不起，我认错人！
I am sorry, I was mistaken

862
00:56:06,238 --> 00:56:07,865
小翠，去拿几个馒头出来
Tracy, take some dumplings out

863
00:56:08,031 --> 00:56:10,576
你认错人了！他不是苏灿
You are mistaken, he is not So Chan

864
00:56:11,743 --> 00:56:13,120
你很像我一个朋友
You are like my friend

865
00:56:13,620 --> 00:56:16,540
以后没东西吃，就到我家取馒头
Come to get some dumplings if you get nothing to eat

866
00:56:17,207 --> 00:56:19,167
我家里人少，吃不完
We always have surplus

867
00:56:20,419 --> 00:56:21,295
馒头来了
Dumplings

868
00:56:21,336 --> 00:56:21,920
拿去
Take it

869
00:56:26,049 --> 00:56:27,593
谢谢⋯
Thank you…

870
00:56:30,387 --> 00:56:30,888
姐姐
Sister,

871
00:56:31,346 --> 00:56:34,516
要不是为了你，他也不会变成这样
he wouldn't be that poor if it were not for you

872
00:56:47,529 --> 00:56:49,823
阿爹！怎么呢
Dad, what are you doing?

873
00:56:49,823 --> 00:56:52,701
阿灿！我刚刚饿坏了
I can't stand the hunger

874
00:56:52,784 --> 00:56:56,413
看见小孩子吃馒头，我借来咬一口
So I bit the dumpling of the kid

875
00:56:56,705 --> 00:56:58,165
我这里有馒头！还给他
I have a dumpling, take it back

876
00:56:58,165 --> 00:56:59,082
这样也可以吗？
Could I pay you another head

877
00:56:59,124 --> 00:57:01,460
我斩了你个头再还给你可不可以？
if I chopped yours

878
00:57:04,171 --> 00:57:05,380
你是状元爷吗？
Are you the Scholar?

879
00:57:07,090 --> 00:57:09,593
是不是？是不是你？
Yes, are you the Scholar?

880
00:57:10,886 --> 00:57:11,637
差点儿是
I was nearly the Scholar

881
00:57:11,637 --> 00:57:13,388
真的！真是状元爷
He is the Scholar!

882
00:57:13,805 --> 00:57:15,515
一定给面子状元爷
We should give him face

883
00:57:16,475 --> 00:57:17,267
多谢⋯多谢
Thank you

884
00:57:17,267 --> 00:57:19,519
等一等！相请不如偶遇
Hold it

885
00:57:21,396 --> 00:57:25,901
相请不如偶遇，是否想请我们喝酒呢
Are they going to treat me some food?

886
00:57:28,904 --> 00:57:29,988
给狗吃的饭到
The dog's rice

887
00:57:30,822 --> 00:57:34,451
状元爷，吃完这饭就放你的爹
Sir, I will let your dad go if you eat the dog's rice now

888
00:57:39,122 --> 00:57:39,873
甚么？
What's the matter?

889
00:57:40,832 --> 00:57:41,625
吃吧
Come on

890
00:57:52,010 --> 00:57:53,637
阿灿！你不能吃
Chan, don't eat that

891
00:57:53,845 --> 00:57:55,472
你吃了后怎样见人？
You can't face the others if you eat this

892
00:57:56,348 --> 00:57:58,100
阿爹年纪大没甚么大不了
Let's forget about me

893
00:57:58,392 --> 00:58:01,228
老兄，说到底我是广州将军
Sir, I was a general in Canton

894
00:58:02,104 --> 00:58:03,021
想怎样呀？
So what?

895
00:58:03,021 --> 00:58:04,773
不要打
Stop fighting

896
00:58:05,190 --> 00:58:05,941
站好
Stand properly

897
00:58:13,323 --> 00:58:15,117
状元爷吃狗的饭
The Scholar eats the dog's food

898
00:58:15,200 --> 00:58:17,953
爹，味道不错
Dad. It's quite delicious

899
00:58:20,539 --> 00:58:22,666
尝尝⋯尝尝，来⋯来
Try some. Come on

900
00:58:26,712 --> 00:58:29,047
好吃，是吗？
It's delicious, isn't it?

901
00:58:33,885 --> 00:58:35,721
阿爹，你看
Dad, look!

902
00:58:36,054 --> 00:58:37,347
有些肉丝在里面
There is a slice of meat here

903
00:58:37,389 --> 00:58:40,058
甚么肉丝？是肉排
It's pork chop!

904
00:58:49,276 --> 00:58:51,528
你俩比狗还要饿！
They are as hungry as dogs!

905
00:58:51,778 --> 00:58:53,572
注定这辈子都吃狗的饭
Enjoy the dog food!

906
00:58:55,991 --> 00:58:58,201
吃吧！快点吧！
Hurry, finish it

907
00:58:59,077 --> 00:59:00,203
这碗饭太好吃了
That's too delicious!

908
00:59:00,746 --> 00:59:02,414
这一口我想留下来作夜宵
I want to save it for midnight snack

909
00:59:02,831 --> 00:59:04,124
多亏你想像得到
It's very clever of you!

910
00:59:04,499 --> 00:59:06,168
真是天生当乞丐的料子
You deserve to be beggars

911
00:59:08,545 --> 00:59:10,172
状元爷都要吃狗的饭
The Scholar is eating dog food

912
00:59:10,172 --> 00:59:11,798
来！我们去吃人的饭吧
Come on, let's go and eat the man's food

913
00:59:16,011 --> 00:59:19,056
苏老伯
Uncle So!

914
00:59:23,769 --> 00:59:24,770
你是⋯
You are…

915
00:59:25,520 --> 00:59:27,189
丐帮帮主就是我爹
My dad was the Master of the Beggars' Association

916
00:59:27,564 --> 00:59:29,733
不如你俩加入丐帮，好不好？
Why don't you join our Beggars' Association

917
00:59:30,067 --> 00:59:31,359
莫大叔，好不好
Uncle Mok, isn't it a good idea?

918
00:59:31,818 --> 00:59:32,152
好
Good

919
00:59:32,152 --> 00:59:33,945
丐帮是不是讨饭帮？
Isn't it the association for beggars?

920
00:59:34,154 --> 00:59:34,696
是
Yes!

921
00:59:34,696 --> 00:59:37,074
正好⋯现在我们当乞丐
That's right, we are being beggars

922
00:59:37,365 --> 00:59:38,992
加入你们丐帮有个照应也好
It's wise to join the Beggars' Association so as to be taken care of

923
00:59:38,992 --> 00:59:40,911
阿灿⋯他去哪儿呢？
Chan… where is that fool going?

924
00:59:40,911 --> 00:59:42,120
阿灿呢？在哪里？
Where is Chan?

925
00:59:42,120 --> 00:59:44,164
好，我们两个报名，两个
OK, we will join you!

926
00:59:44,164 --> 00:59:46,458
灿⋯灿
Chan… Chan…

927
00:59:58,553 --> 01:00:00,180
如霜！恭喜发财
Yushang, good year!

928
01:00:01,473 --> 01:00:03,350
莫大叔！恭喜发财
Uncle Mok, happy new year!

929
01:00:03,600 --> 01:00:04,893
这礼物是给你的
This is for you

930
01:00:05,102 --> 01:00:06,686
多谢！多谢
Thank you

931
01:00:08,605 --> 01:00:11,149
这两件衣服，一件给你，一件给阿灿
One cloth is for you and the other is for Chan

932
01:00:11,942 --> 01:00:13,652
先把东西放下，先把东西放下
Thank you. Put it down first

933
01:00:15,112 --> 01:00:15,904
有没有零钱？
Do you have any coins?

934
01:00:15,946 --> 01:00:16,738
有
Yes!

935
01:00:16,780 --> 01:00:18,573
有就拿来！来⋯　　干甚么？
- Give them to me, come on    - What for?

936
01:00:19,282 --> 01:00:22,828
干甚么？过新年当然要利利是是
It's new year, you should receive a red packet

937
01:00:22,953 --> 01:00:24,788
来，祝你身体健康
Come on, happy new year

938
01:00:24,830 --> 01:00:25,705
恭喜发财
Good year!

939
01:00:25,705 --> 01:00:27,207
你就青春美丽　　谢谢
- Wish you ever beauty    - Thank you

940
01:00:27,207 --> 01:00:29,167
莫大叔，我们二老就两免了
Uncle Mok, we needn't give red packets to each other

941
01:00:29,167 --> 01:00:30,252
阿灿呢？
How about Chan

942
01:00:30,460 --> 01:00:34,881
阿灿？他由年三十睡到大年初一
Chan?

943
01:00:34,881 --> 01:00:36,007
还没睡醒
He is still sleeping

944
01:00:36,216 --> 01:00:38,552
他刚刚才睡！别把他吵醒
Don't wake him up

945
01:00:39,469 --> 01:00:40,971
我做年糕给大家吃吧
I will cook you some new year cake

946
01:00:41,596 --> 01:00:44,099
好！我帮你
Let me help you

947
01:00:45,642 --> 01:00:47,769
新年还在睡觉
How can he sleep on the 1st day of this year?

948
01:00:49,271 --> 01:00:50,730
真是没用的家伙！
He is useless

949
01:00:53,316 --> 01:00:54,442
大家到齐了没？
Are you all here?

950
01:00:55,902 --> 01:00:58,655
对付赵无极一定要团结丐帮
To fight against Chiu, we need a union of the Beggar's Association

951
01:00:59,656 --> 01:01:02,367
我们要选出新帮主来主持大局
So we must choose a new master to be in charge of the association

952
01:01:03,243 --> 01:01:05,287
如霜⋯如霜
Yushang…

953
01:01:06,371 --> 01:01:08,081
对付三位长老的莲花落阵
To defeat the Lotus position of the three seniors

954
01:01:08,456 --> 01:01:09,374
全靠你了
You should try your best

955
01:01:10,083 --> 01:01:13,086
莫大叔！莲花落阵你也没把握
Uncle, I don't have faith to defeat them

956
01:01:13,461 --> 01:01:15,338
以我现在打狗棒法的功力
Judging from my kung-fu now,

957
01:01:15,547 --> 01:01:18,300
怎么可能打败三位长老当上帮主呢？
how can I defeat them and become the new master?

958
01:01:19,676 --> 01:01:23,013
这颗大还丹，你吃了之后会功力大增
Take this Taiwan pill, after this, your power will be improved

959
01:01:23,513 --> 01:01:26,683
不行！这颗大还丹是给你治内伤用的
No, this is the only medicine to cure your inner injury

960
01:01:26,683 --> 01:01:27,726
我怎么能吃呢？
How can I take this?

961
01:01:28,018 --> 01:01:29,311
不用担心不用担心
Don't worry,

962
01:01:29,644 --> 01:01:31,605
想找人比武可以找我儿子
you can ask my son to fight for you

963
01:01:31,605 --> 01:01:33,315
我儿子怎么说也是一个武状元
He was a scholar of Martial Arts

964
01:01:33,315 --> 01:01:33,982
现在⋯
before…

965
01:01:34,024 --> 01:01:35,108
⋯不！曾经
Before…

966
01:01:35,400 --> 01:01:36,943
你看他懒洋洋的
Look at him, he is so lazy,

967
01:01:36,985 --> 01:01:39,112
只会睡觉，怎能打架呢？
he knows sleeping only

968
01:01:39,404 --> 01:01:41,323
连当乞丐的资格都没有
He is not even qualified to be a beggar!

969
01:01:41,364 --> 01:01:43,241
你别那么坦白行不行？
Don't be that frank, can you?

970
01:01:44,201 --> 01:01:46,203
你别那么大声好不好？
Don't shout that loudly, OK?

971
01:01:54,419 --> 01:01:59,007
阿灿，不管人家现在怎么看不起你
Chan, no matter how they despise you,

972
01:02:00,675 --> 01:02:02,552
老爹对你很有信心
I have faith in you

973
01:02:03,595 --> 01:02:05,597
虽然现在你没有武功
Although you lost your power

974
01:02:06,306 --> 01:02:07,682
但是以你的底子
With your background,

975
01:02:08,058 --> 01:02:09,476
只要你肯出一点点力
only if you try hard,

976
01:02:09,768 --> 01:02:11,394
必定会有一番作为
you can achieve something

977
01:02:11,770 --> 01:02:13,855
我现在已经没有力，也不想再用力
But I am now powerless, I don't want to fight again

978
01:02:13,855 --> 01:02:15,106
怎么会没有力呢？
You have power!

979
01:02:15,398 --> 01:02:16,274
快打我一拳
Come on, beat me

980
01:02:20,445 --> 01:02:21,905
这一拳蛮有力吗
See, that was powerful

981
01:02:22,155 --> 01:02:23,782
所以我说，做人⋯
Well, being a people…

982
01:02:23,949 --> 01:02:25,951
算了！不要再浪费时间
Forget it, don't waste time

983
01:02:25,951 --> 01:02:27,410
还是让我多睡一会儿吧
Why don't you let me sleep?

984
01:02:33,416 --> 01:02:34,501
你怎么把门锁上？
Why did you lock the door?

985
01:02:34,542 --> 01:02:35,835
你慢慢睡吧
Enjoy sleeping

986
01:02:50,350 --> 01:02:54,271
孩儿，我费尽心思才弄出这么大阵容
Son, I tried very hard to get this for you

987
01:02:54,729 --> 01:02:57,941
你要多用点心把打狗棒法练好才行
Try hard to practise, be good

988
01:03:20,588 --> 01:03:21,881
你爬得那么高干甚么？
Why do you go up?

989
01:03:22,757 --> 01:03:24,426
就算你要我练打狗棒法
Even you want me to practise Kung-fu,

990
01:03:25,093 --> 01:03:26,886
你总该留个棒子给我吧
you should give me a waddy first

991
01:03:28,388 --> 01:03:30,515
抱歉抱歉！你接好了
I am sorry, catch it

992
01:03:38,690 --> 01:03:41,318
天将降大任于斯人也
Before being appointed an important task,

993
01:03:41,526 --> 01:03:47,032
必先劳其筋骨，饿其体肤，苦其心智
God will give you severe training for soul and flesh.

994
01:03:53,955 --> 01:03:56,791
苦海无涯？你写的？
Did you write it?

995
01:03:57,375 --> 01:04:02,714
写得这么丑，把它擦掉也对
It's ugly, it's right to wipe it away

996
01:04:05,550 --> 01:04:06,509
乞丐？
Hey, beggar?

997
01:04:06,509 --> 01:04:07,010
是
Yes

998
01:04:07,510 --> 01:04:08,636
我也是
Me too

999
01:04:08,636 --> 01:04:09,429
恭喜你
Congratulations

1000
01:04:11,639 --> 01:04:13,099
有没有东西吃？　　没有
- Is there anything to eat?    - No

1001
01:04:13,683 --> 01:04:15,060
正好我有
Luckily, I have

1002
01:04:20,774 --> 01:04:24,944
这造型不去讨饭博人家同情，真可惜
See your look, it's a waste for you not to beg

1003
01:04:25,236 --> 01:04:26,446
这与你无关！
None of your damn business

1004
01:04:27,655 --> 01:04:29,032
你当乞丐也这么懒
You are too lazy to be a beggar!

1005
01:04:29,282 --> 01:04:31,284
同行都瞧不起你了
Your fellows despise you

1006
01:04:33,036 --> 01:04:34,913
我以前到那里都被人家看重
I was always respected by others

1007
01:04:35,288 --> 01:04:36,664
还不是落得这个下场
But now, I am despised

1008
01:04:37,374 --> 01:04:38,792
我正好刚刚相反
Dislike from you,

1009
01:04:39,042 --> 01:04:41,169
我一辈子没被人瞧得起过
no one respected me before

1010
01:04:41,795 --> 01:04:44,589
听我说，先别走，听我说
Listen to me. Don't go!

1011
01:04:45,215 --> 01:04:49,052
记得有一次，在广东
I remembered once in Canton

1012
01:04:49,344 --> 01:04:52,180
请我吃饭喝酒嫖妓过夜
A fool paid my living, including hooking

1013
01:04:52,222 --> 01:04:53,848
这样的人也有
What a weird man

1014
01:04:56,434 --> 01:04:58,061
帅哥，我记得你
Kid, I remembered you

1015
01:04:59,020 --> 01:05:01,356
臭小子，我也记得你
Me too

1016
01:05:01,398 --> 01:05:02,315
废话少说
Hey, hurry up

1017
01:05:02,357 --> 01:05:03,775
还我钱让我顶一下
Repay my money, I am in urgent need

1018
01:05:03,817 --> 01:05:05,110
如果我有钱
If I had money,

1019
01:05:05,318 --> 01:05:07,862
我也不用在这儿挨馒头
I wouldn't be a beggar!

1020
01:05:11,491 --> 01:05:14,077
不过你不用怕，你有恩于我
But, don't worry, you were my benefactor,

1021
01:05:14,285 --> 01:05:15,829
我会报答你的
I will repay you one day

1022
01:05:16,955 --> 01:05:18,540
多谢，心领
Thank you very much

1023
01:05:19,999 --> 01:05:21,334
给你钱也没有用
But, you can't buy back what you lost

1024
01:05:21,751 --> 01:05:23,420
也买不回你失去的东西
even if you have money again

1025
01:05:24,754 --> 01:05:25,547
我失去了甚么？
What did I lose?

1026
01:05:26,131 --> 01:05:28,216
尊严，自信
Pride and faith

1027
01:05:28,716 --> 01:05:30,009
还有你心爱的女人
And your woman too

1028
01:05:32,554 --> 01:05:33,680
你究竟是何人？
Who are you?

1029
01:05:34,097 --> 01:05:37,892
好说，在下洪日新，外号老鬼新
I am Hung Yat-sun, nicknamed Old Bag Sun

1030
01:05:38,268 --> 01:05:41,354
乞丐中辈份最高，字号最老
I am the most senior one among the beggars

1031
01:05:41,604 --> 01:05:42,814
做乞丐有甚么不好？
It's good to be a beggar

1032
01:05:43,314 --> 01:05:44,941
想走就走，想睡就睡
You can do everything you want

1033
01:05:45,150 --> 01:05:46,151
你也可以一样吗
You can do the same

1034
01:05:46,401 --> 01:05:49,279
你说，你想要甚么？我成全你
Tell me, what do you want? I will make your wish come true

1035
01:05:49,571 --> 01:05:50,697
我想重新做人
I want to be human again

1036
01:05:50,738 --> 01:05:52,365
怎么你觉得你不像人吗？
Don't you think you are not human-like?

1037
01:05:53,575 --> 01:05:54,868
一直都不算是
Not at all

1038
01:05:55,326 --> 01:05:57,704
所以你才会弄成这样，年青人
So you have to be a beggar now

1039
01:06:00,248 --> 01:06:02,625
非常好，非常好
Very good! Very good!

1040
01:06:03,376 --> 01:06:06,838
实不相瞒，我看阁下从头到脚趾头
But I won't cheat you, from your head to toes

1041
01:06:06,838 --> 01:06:09,174
没有一个地方不露乞丐形格
Every part of you is beggar-like

1042
01:06:10,467 --> 01:06:11,176
又如何？
So what?

1043
01:06:11,217 --> 01:06:14,012
即是说阁下注定讨饭讨一辈子
That means, you will be a beggar for your life

1044
01:06:17,015 --> 01:06:18,975
还是不跟你说，我想睡一会儿
I don't want to talk to you, I want to sleep first

1045
01:06:19,434 --> 01:06:21,603
先别走！行行出状元
Don't go, you can achieve in your profession

1046
01:06:21,811 --> 01:06:22,937
如果我没看错
From my judgement,

1047
01:06:22,937 --> 01:06:24,564
你会是乞丐中的霸主
you will be the king of beggars

1048
01:06:25,064 --> 01:06:27,692
乞丐中的霸主？那是甚么？
King of beggars, what does that mean?

1049
01:06:29,319 --> 01:06:30,069
还是乞丐
That is beggar

1050
01:06:34,532 --> 01:06:36,576
我不管你是甚么人，我不想再跟你说
I won't care who you are, I just want to stop the conversation

1051
01:06:36,576 --> 01:06:38,661
请你让开，不要碍著我睡觉
Please step aside, don't stop me from sleeping

1052
01:06:39,287 --> 01:06:40,121
你找死吧？
Damn you!

1053
01:06:40,121 --> 01:06:41,664
不是⋯你说要睡觉
No… I just want to sleep

1054
01:06:41,664 --> 01:06:42,999
我只想跟你一块儿
with you

1055
01:06:43,625 --> 01:06:45,043
神经病
Idiot!

1056
01:06:48,755 --> 01:06:51,966
年青人，我们梦中相见
Kid, see you in the dream

1057
01:07:02,644 --> 01:07:05,438
佛前金座，罗汉归位
Before the Buddha, the Disciples return to your position

1058
01:07:06,481 --> 01:07:09,984
降龙，伏虎
To suppress the dragon and tiger

1059
01:07:16,783 --> 01:07:19,285
苏灿，你享尽人间富贵
So Chan, you enjoyed the prosperity of the world

1060
01:07:19,577 --> 01:07:21,162
亦尝尽人间苦楚
And you tasted the bitter fruit of the world too

1061
01:07:21,579 --> 01:07:22,956
如今大彻大悟
Now you regret it

1062
01:07:23,248 --> 01:07:26,084
我就以洪七公第七代传人的身份
On behalf of Master Hung

1063
01:07:26,209 --> 01:07:27,627
封你为睡梦罗汉
I appoint you to be the “Sleeping Disciple”

1064
01:07:28,086 --> 01:07:31,339
醉回梦生法，传授你睡梦罗汉拳
Now, I will teach you the “Sleeping Disciple's Fist”!

1065
01:07:31,589 --> 01:07:34,509
希望你好好利用，接招
Hope you can make good use of it. Come on

1066
01:07:39,222 --> 01:07:43,393
前辈⋯
Senior…

1067
01:07:48,731 --> 01:07:51,401
苦尽甘来？
The bitter past

1068
01:07:56,030 --> 01:08:00,368
万岁！万岁！万万岁
Long life to you…

1069
01:08:02,495 --> 01:08:05,415
白羊降世，天理循环
Here comes the White Goat

1070
01:08:05,832 --> 01:08:10,211
真空家乡，无生老母，赐我神通
My mother, give me power

1071
01:08:10,545 --> 01:08:11,921
超渡众生
To save the people!

1072
01:08:33,026 --> 01:08:34,902
皇帝明天会到成都狩猎
Tomorrow the Emperor will go hunting

1073
01:08:35,862 --> 01:08:38,239
我会用献上美女的理由接近他
I will send him a pretty girl, so as to get close to him

1074
01:08:39,782 --> 01:08:43,202
宛玲，你明天可能要牺牲一下色相
Yuen Ling, you should seduce him tomorrow

1075
01:08:43,703 --> 01:08:44,579
是
Yes

1076
01:08:45,997 --> 01:08:47,457
只要明天杀了皇帝
If we can kill the Emperor,

1077
01:08:48,249 --> 01:08:49,626
天下就尽在我手
I can take over his reign

1078
01:08:50,251 --> 01:08:52,837
荣华富贵绝对少不了你们
I will give you a share of wealth!

1079
01:08:57,592 --> 01:09:01,262
万岁！万岁！万万岁
Long life to you

1080
01:09:01,763 --> 01:09:02,305
长老
Senior!

1081
01:09:02,597 --> 01:09:03,473
回去再说
Let's go back now

1082
01:09:35,546 --> 01:09:36,297
长老
Senior!

1083
01:09:36,297 --> 01:09:37,298
我们走
Let's go!

1084
01:09:50,353 --> 01:09:51,229
长老
Senior!

1085
01:10:30,560 --> 01:10:31,769
我们追　　不用追了！
- Let's chase them    - Stop!

1086
01:10:33,271 --> 01:10:34,397
皇上快要出发
The Emperor is setting off soon

1087
01:10:35,648 --> 01:10:36,691
你杀了我的女人⋯
You killed a woman…

1088
01:10:37,024 --> 01:10:38,484
⋯我要把你献给皇上
You should replace her as a gift to the Emperor!

1089
01:10:44,866 --> 01:10:47,577
怎么？没有人敢上来当帮主
No one dares come up to fight for the leadership?

1090
01:10:47,702 --> 01:10:50,079
叫莫老三把打狗棒交出来
Ask Mok to give us the “Dog Hitting Waddy”!

1091
01:10:57,295 --> 01:10:59,422
莫大叔跟你姐姐到底到哪处？
Where have they been?

1092
01:11:00,047 --> 01:11:01,215
我怎么知道
I don't know,

1093
01:11:01,716 --> 01:11:04,260
刚才我听见莫大叔跟姐姐说了几句话
I saw them chat,

1094
01:11:04,260 --> 01:11:05,178
就出去了
then they went away

1095
01:11:07,555 --> 01:11:08,973
难道他俩有暧昧关系？
Is there any affair between them?

1096
01:11:20,735 --> 01:11:22,278
现在开始选帮主
Now, we are going to choose the new leader

1097
01:11:28,659 --> 01:11:29,702
莫大叔⋯
Uncle Mok…

1098
01:11:29,702 --> 01:11:30,787
真的被你嚇我一跳
I am scared,

1099
01:11:30,787 --> 01:11:31,621
还以为你不会来了
I think you won't come back

1100
01:11:31,621 --> 01:11:33,289
没事吗？　　姐姐呢？
- How is it?    - Where is sister?

1101
01:11:33,790 --> 01:11:35,666
你姐姐给赵无极抓了
Your sister is caught by Chiu

1102
01:11:36,042 --> 01:11:38,377
我们要找人上去选帮主
We'd better find someone to compete for the leadership

1103
01:11:44,091 --> 01:11:46,177
到底派谁上去呢？
Who should go?

1104
01:12:00,274 --> 01:12:00,942
让我去
I'll do it

1105
01:12:00,942 --> 01:12:01,734
莫大叔
Uncle Mok

1106
01:12:01,901 --> 01:12:03,194
不如让我试试
Why don't you let me try?

1107
01:12:40,898 --> 01:12:41,691
阿灿
Chan,

1108
01:12:43,818 --> 01:12:46,070
你不是九代弟子，快下来
you are not qualified, come down

1109
01:12:47,321 --> 01:12:50,366
既然你挑不出好的，我可以教育你！
Since you don't have a good candidate, I'll give you some advantage

1110
01:12:50,783 --> 01:12:52,785
阿灿，你不要以为好玩
Chan, it's not a game

1111
01:12:53,119 --> 01:12:54,912
你会没命的！快下来
You will be killed, come down

1112
01:12:55,162 --> 01:12:57,999
没相干，我的命早就当没了
It doesn't matter, I have forgotten my life already

1113
01:12:58,207 --> 01:12:59,709
废话！丢他
Bullshit, throw him to death

1114
01:13:09,176 --> 01:13:11,262
既然如此，我就成全你
Well, I will make your wish come true

1115
01:13:39,624 --> 01:13:40,166
他在干吗？
What is he doing?

1116
01:13:40,166 --> 01:13:40,917
睡觉？
Sleeping

1117
01:13:56,015 --> 01:13:57,433
这一招难道就是⋯
Isn't this stance…

1118
01:13:58,434 --> 01:14:00,603
新师叔的睡梦罗汉拳？
Uncle Sun's “Sleeping Disciple's Fists”?

1119
01:14:01,479 --> 01:14:02,396
布阵
Set the position!

1120
01:14:18,329 --> 01:14:19,497
天亮了没有
Is it dawn?

1121
01:15:18,514 --> 01:15:19,724
各位不好意思
I am sorry!

1122
01:15:19,974 --> 01:15:20,766
我赢了
I won

1123
01:15:21,058 --> 01:15:22,143
你打赢我们有甚么用？
What is the use for defeating us?

1124
01:15:22,309 --> 01:15:23,602
你又不会打狗棒法
You don't know how to use the “Dog Hitting Waddy”.

1125
01:15:24,395 --> 01:15:25,604
你不配当帮主
You are not qualified to be the leader of us

1126
01:15:28,733 --> 01:15:30,067
打狗棒！是吗
“Dog Hitting Waddy”?

1127
01:15:34,739 --> 01:15:36,115
棒棒都打狗
It's for hitting dogs

1128
01:15:37,533 --> 01:15:39,660
谁说我不会打狗棒法？
I do know how to use this waddy!

1129
01:15:39,702 --> 01:15:40,995
不像打狗棒法
But it's different from the standard stances!

1130
01:15:41,120 --> 01:15:41,996
也蛮厉害！
It's quite powerful!

1131
01:15:46,625 --> 01:15:48,502
他打断了打狗棒
He broke the waddy!

1132
01:15:50,129 --> 01:15:52,965
他打断我们镇帮之宝！我们杀了他
He broke the treasure of our Association, let's kill him!

1133
01:16:06,562 --> 01:16:09,065
洪七公在此谁敢放肆
I am Master Hung, who dares go against me?

1134
01:16:09,982 --> 01:16:11,859
我当年定下帮规
I set the rules of the association

1135
01:16:12,318 --> 01:16:14,695
任何弟子破了莲花落阵
Any student who defeated the Lotus Position

1136
01:16:15,029 --> 01:16:16,822
都有资格当帮主
could be the leader

1137
01:16:17,114 --> 01:16:18,824
你们是不是全忘掉了？
Have you all forgotten?

1138
01:16:19,325 --> 01:16:21,744
丐帮之所以成为天下第一大帮
We becomes the biggest association

1139
01:16:21,952 --> 01:16:23,579
全因为团结两个字
because of being united

1140
01:16:24,121 --> 01:16:26,373
我洪某当年留下打狗棒
I left you the “Dog Hitting Waddy”,

1141
01:16:26,373 --> 01:16:28,876
目的只是留给大家作为留念
