如霜
Yushang

1366
01:35:42,570 --> 01:35:44,614
你记不记得我们之间还有一个协议
We have an agreement, do you remember?

1367
01:35:45,573 --> 01:35:49,244
记得！一人之下！万人之上
Yes, be the top of all

1368
01:35:49,285 --> 01:35:51,329
盖世武功！状元之才
Invincible

1369
01:35:51,537 --> 01:35:53,164
可惜我始终都当不成状元
But, I can't be the Scholar

1370
01:35:53,498 --> 01:35:56,251
是！不过我不喜欢状元
But I don't like Scholar at all

1371
01:35:56,584 --> 01:35:58,253
我喜欢乞丐嘛
I love beggars.

1372
01:36:00,004 --> 01:36:01,422
你先！我稍后跟上
You first, I will go after you

1373
01:36:14,686 --> 01:36:18,106
僧格林参，你竟不分青红皂白
Seng-ko-lin-ch'in, you are really a fool

1374
01:36:18,815 --> 01:36:19,941
你引狼入室
You bring a thief to harm me

1375
01:36:20,316 --> 01:36:22,277
朕现在贬你为小乞丐
Now, you are titled to be a beggar

1376
01:36:22,610 --> 01:36:25,113
你当乞丐很好，看你的样子很有天分
You have potential to be a beggar

1377
01:36:25,697 --> 01:36:26,781
明天到城隍庙报到
Report duty in the temple tomorrow

1378
01:36:27,573 --> 01:36:28,866
有事报我的名字就行
If there is anyone bullies you, just tell them my name

1379
01:36:30,576 --> 01:36:32,829
多谢帮主，多谢帮主关照
Thank you, thank you master

1380
01:36:33,037 --> 01:36:36,124
苏灿，你有甚么要求？
So Chan, what do you want as reward?

1381
01:36:38,710 --> 01:36:40,044
你真没话跟朕说？
Don't you have anything to tell me?

1382
01:36:44,215 --> 01:36:46,175
有甚么好说呢？走
Nothing special, let's go

1383
01:36:47,093 --> 01:36:47,844
抱我起来
Pick me up

1384
01:36:49,137 --> 01:36:50,722
苏英雄！苏英雄
Mister So!

1385
01:36:50,805 --> 01:36:51,681
放下来
Put me down

1386
01:36:52,390 --> 01:36:53,391
你别以为救过朕
Although you have saved me,

1387
01:36:53,808 --> 01:36:56,144
你对朕不敬，朕一样会杀了你
if you don't respect me, I will kill you

1388
01:36:56,894 --> 01:36:59,647
你要杀我就不会这样跟我说话
If so, you needn't squat to talk to me

1389
01:36:59,939 --> 01:37:02,650
不要动，否则还碍眼
Don't move, it'll attract their attention

1390
01:37:05,528 --> 01:37:07,322
其实我跟你没醪没轕
Actually we have no relation,

1391
01:37:07,322 --> 01:37:08,990
真没甚么好谈
we have nothing to chat about

1392
01:37:09,407 --> 01:37:10,783
你丐帮弟子几千万
You have billions of fellows.

1393
01:37:10,992 --> 01:37:13,453
你一天不解散，朕怎么安心？
Your force makes me worry

1394
01:37:14,329 --> 01:37:16,372
丐帮有多少弟子不是由我决定
The number of fellows doesn't depend on me,

1395
01:37:16,372 --> 01:37:17,540
而是由你决定
but you

1396
01:37:17,832 --> 01:37:18,750
我？
What?

1397
01:37:19,751 --> 01:37:22,670
如果你真的英明神武，令到国泰民安
If you are great, making the society peaceful and wealthy,

1398
01:37:23,129 --> 01:37:24,922
谁会愿意当乞丐？
no one wishes to be a beggar, right?

1399
01:37:27,300 --> 01:37:29,552
有道理，有道理　　好自为之吧
- It's reasonable    - Be smart

1400
01:37:30,261 --> 01:37:31,012
不过
But,

1401
