揹著女儿，博取同情？
You beg with your girl, you think I'll give you money out of mercy?

1408
01:37:51,199 --> 01:37:52,825
是！施舍点吧
Yes, please give me money

1409
01:37:52,867 --> 01:37:54,994
乞丐就是不给！快滚
No mercy, go away

1410
01:37:55,078 --> 01:37:55,912
不给不行
No, you should pay me

1411
01:37:56,287 --> 01:37:57,372
应份的！兄弟
It's a must, pal

1412
01:37:58,623 --> 01:38:01,167
奉旨乞食？有没有搅错？
A must? Kidding?

1413
01:38:01,417 --> 01:38:03,836
没有搅错！爽手点！
It's true, be quick

1414
01:38:03,836 --> 01:38:04,670
怕了你
It's bad luck to meet you

1415
01:38:05,004 --> 01:38:06,089
先别走
Stop

1416
