又怎么？
What?

1417
01:38:07,215 --> 01:38:10,343
还有一家大小的！给多点
See my family? Give more

1418
01:38:10,468 --> 01:38:11,552
添多少？
How much?

1419
01:38:11,594 --> 01:38:13,554
没有一千都给八百
Not less than a thousand, got me?

1420
01:38:17,767 --> 01:38:19,102
还不快谢谢人家？
Say thank you now

1421
01:38:20,436 --> 01:38:21,354
谢谢
Thank you, uncle

1422
01:38:21,437 --> 01:38:23,272
快点吃吧
Hurry up

1423
